[
  {
    "key": "4c466211804d677d990b003f662c59f990211ca45894ce60168d37add59fb563",
    "original": " Perk Point.",
    "translation": "",
    "context": "\"Gain \" + getroottable().MSU.Text.colorPositive(\"+1\") + \" Perk Point.\""
  },
  {
    "key": "e85bcaf24f59768247d6f10cbcd2c7e7622609a3735594fa734a498d1215b6ed",
    "original": " [Action Points|Concept.ActionPoints] and builds ",
    "translation": "",
    "context": "\"When starting your [turn|Concept.Turn] with a spear equipped, the first piercing spear attack costs \" + getroottable().MSU.Text.colorPositive(\"no\") + \" [Action Points|Concept.ActionPoints] and builds \" + getroottable().MSU.Text.colorPositive(\"50%\") + \" less [Fatigue|Concept.Fatigue]. This expires upon moving from your position if using a two-handed spear, or moving more than 1 tile if using a one-handed spear.\""
  },
  {
    "key": "e85bcaf24f59768247d6f10cbcd2c7e7622609a3735594fa734a498d1215b6ed",
    "original": " [Action Points|Concept.ActionPoints] and builds ",
    "translation": "",
    "context": "\"When using a throwing weapon which uses ammo, whenever you end your movement over an enemy's corpse during your [turn|Concept.Turn], recover \" + getroottable().MSU.Text.colorPositive(1) + \" ammo. Immediately afterward, the next throwing attack costs \" + getroottable().MSU.Text.colorPositive(\"no\") + \" [Action Points|Concept.ActionPoints] and builds \" + getroottable().MSU.Text.colorPositive(\"50%\") + \" less [Fatigue|Concept.Fatigue].\""
  },
  {
    "key": "c17de604ab22b52ec29586e5eca6fdc359543c94953ec3680cd2d34af3dd7fac",
    "original": " [Action Points|Concept.ActionPoints] as long as they start their [turn|Concept.Turn] adjacent to you.",
    "translation": "",
    "context": "\"Any ally who is adjacent to an enemy, or is adjacent to an ally who is adjacent to an enemy, gains \" + getroottable().MSU.Text.colorPositive(\"+3\") + \" [Action Points|Concept.ActionPoints] as long as they start their [turn|Concept.Turn] adjacent to you.\""
  },
  {
    "key": "3586ffb45a12d7e607b1b8e4116185c8f193a85cbc498535613a577a0fda273b",
    "original": " [Action Points|Concept.ActionPoints] each.",
    "translation": "",
    "context": "\"The first 2 [fatalities|Concept.Fatality] during your [turn|Concept.Turn] instantly restore \" + getroottable().MSU.Text.colorPositive(3) + \" [Action Points|Concept.ActionPoints] each.\""
  },
  {
    "key": "626b3046a0b942d31ca3c2e71c6ea47c1ec7eb419beecb34dddcaf4a8a4f1204",
    "original": " [Action Points|Concept.ActionPoints] to [$ $|Skill+reload_bolt], just like regular crossbows, allowing you to shoot, reload and move.",
    "translation": "",
    "context": "\"[$ $|Item+heavy_crossbow] now require \" + getroottable().MSU.Text.colorNegative(\"4\") + \" [Action Points|Concept.ActionPoints] to [$ $|Skill+reload_bolt], just like regular crossbows, allowing you to shoot, reload and move.\""
  },
  {
    "key": "8d0ad52cc041f172a9ff9f04b20592c8d9d630be4da6c853b8eca7ae30aabe7c",
    "original": " [Action Points|Concept.ActionPoints] to [$ $|Skill+reload_handgonne_skill] and can be fired every turn instead of every other turn.",
    "translation": "",
    "context": "\"[$ $|Item+handgonne] now require \" + getroottable().MSU.Text.colorNegative(\"6\") + \" [Action Points|Concept.ActionPoints] to [$ $|Skill+reload_handgonne_skill] and can be fired every turn instead of every other turn.\""
  },
  {
    "key": "fa27fce7cdcaeed5c64d439f161e09259a10c9db8d6d6e0c482355b42b301e67",
    "original": " [Action Points|Concept.ActionPoints].",
    "translation": "",
    "context": "\"When you use [Wait|Concept.Wait], recover [Action Points|Concept.ActionPoints] until you have \" + getroottable().MSU.Text.colorPositive(\"4\") + \" [Action Points|Concept.ActionPoints].\""
  },
  {
    "key": "fa27fce7cdcaeed5c64d439f161e09259a10c9db8d6d6e0c482355b42b301e67",
    "original": " [Action Points|Concept.ActionPoints].",
    "translation": "",
    "context": "\"Once per [turn|Concept.Turn], after you use a skill targeting an adjacent ally, recover \" + getroottable().MSU.Text.colorPositive(\"3\") + \" [Action Points|Concept.ActionPoints].\""
  },
  {
    "key": "1f02dd4c2b112f60cce431da51b7732689448b7e95841a2d94c48ffb8e1280d3",
    "original": " [Fatigue|Concept.Fatigue] cost.",
    "translation": "",
    "context": "\"Unlocks the [$ $|Skill+rf_passing_step_skill] skill which, immediately after a successful attack, allows you to move one tile ignoring [Zone of Control|Concept.ZoneOfControl] with reduced [Action Point|Concept.ActionPoints] cost but \" + getroottable().MSU.Text.colorNegative(\"+2\") + \" [Fatigue|Concept.Fatigue] cost.\""
  },
  {
    "key": "d223dd81d1a476f47dba2324e429ce9c95255b434eed6748907259ab4a683122",
    "original": " [Fatigue|Concept.Fatigue] remaining, but this does not cost any [Action Points|Concept.ActionPoints] nor builds any [Fatigue|Concept.Fatigue].",
    "translation": "",
    "context": "\"You only gain the free [$ $|Skill+riposte_effect] or [$ $|Perk+perk_rf_rebuke] if you have at least \" + getroottable().MSU.Text.colorNegative(15) + \" [Fatigue|Concept.Fatigue] remaining, but this does not cost any [Action Points|Concept.ActionPoints] nor builds any [Fatigue|Concept.Fatigue].\""
  },
  {
    "key": "5e5e7f6fd6f937bf3d3044c74589681f1a8ba505a4125314b60cef89b9420879",
    "original": " [Initiative|Concept.Initiative] and ",
    "translation": "",
    "context": "\"Whenever you attack or are attacked, hit or miss, gain a stacking \" + getroottable().MSU.Text.colorPositive(\"+5\") + \" [Initiative|Concept.Initiative] and \" + getroottable().MSU.Text.colorPositive(\"+5%\") + \" reduction to the [Fatigue|Concept.Fatigue] cost of skills until the end of your next [turn|Concept.Turn], up to a maximum of \" + getroottable().MSU.Text.colorPositive(\"+25\") + \" and \" + getroottable().MSU.Text.colorPositive(\"+25%\") + \" respectively.\""
  },
  {
    "key": "97b26ede269b802ec059d4271f52c3f593b17bb9db2aa6000d12a5503f7fb677",
    "original": " [Melee Defense|Concept.MeleeDefense] against enemies attacked by your partner, for one [turn|Concept.Turn].",
    "translation": "",
    "context": "\"Gain \" + getroottable().MSU.Text.colorPositive(\"+10\") + \" [Melee Skill|Concept.MeleeSkill] against enemies that attack your partner, and \" + getroottable().MSU.Text.colorPositive(\"+10\") + \" [Melee Defense|Concept.MeleeDefense] against enemies attacked by your partner, for one [turn|Concept.Turn].\""
  },
  {
    "key": "77543fbebc53c983b34825c80c5ac1fd4e2d0393042498390adb9f87e1d817c2",
    "original": " [Melee Skill|Concept.MeleeSkill] against enemies that attack your partner, and ",
    "translation": "",
    "context": "\"Gain \" + getroottable().MSU.Text.colorPositive(\"+10\") + \" [Melee Skill|Concept.MeleeSkill] against enemies that attack your partner, and \" + getroottable().MSU.Text.colorPositive(\"+10\") + \" [Melee Defense|Concept.MeleeDefense] against enemies attacked by your partner, for one [turn|Concept.Turn].\""
  },
  {
    "key": "b5c74adbb7593c5c2f067d75cf4d06aa9255d3b9e606c7db7ff0d7eaee2a6a74",
    "original": " [Melee Skill|Concept.MeleeSkill] and [Melee Defense|Concept.MeleeDefense] against that opponent for the remainder of the combat.",
    "translation": "",
    "context": "\"Every time an opponent attacks you in melee or you attack an opponent, gain a stacking \" + getroottable().MSU.Text.colorPositive(\"+3\") + \" [Melee Skill|Concept.MeleeSkill] and [Melee Defense|Concept.MeleeDefense] against that opponent for the remainder of the combat.\""
  },
  {
    "key": "6af97be82a27766e4bf2ccaccf7775cb64611213c9a588a0b0519d8bc861f6d2",
    "original": " [Melee Skill|Concept.MeleeSkill] and [Melee Defense|Concept.MeleeDefense] and ",
    "translation": "",
    "context": "\"Gain \" + getroottable().MSU.Text.colorPositive(\"+1\") + \" [Melee Skill|Concept.MeleeSkill] and [Melee Defense|Concept.MeleeDefense] and \" + getroottable().MSU.Text.colorPositive(\"+1%\") + \" additional damage ignoring armor per character level.\""
  },
  {
    "key": "5ab8af7224ccb678fc92c75644b88f8e9c228b76c11e00e6591b66a6b9ec14a4",
    "original": " [Melee Skill|Concept.MeleeSkill], [Ranged Skill|Concept.RangeSkill], [Melee Defense|Concept.MeleeDefense] and [Ranged Defense|Concept.RangeDefense] and ",
    "translation": "",
    "context": "\"For each adjacent ally, gain \" + getroottable().MSU.Text.colorPositive(\"+2\") + \" [Melee Skill|Concept.MeleeSkill], [Ranged Skill|Concept.RangeSkill], [Melee Defense|Concept.MeleeDefense] and [Ranged Defense|Concept.RangeDefense] and \" + getroottable().MSU.Text.colorPositive(\"+5\") + \" [Resolve|Concept.Bravery].\""
  },
  {
    "key": "2eaed548ec01c04e77686b21c23c4381d3a41835e660b0947b938855f41e0373",
    "original": " [Ranged Skill|Concept.RangeSkill], [Ranged Defense|Concept.RangeDefense], and [Resolve|Concept.Bravery]. The bonus increases by ",
    "translation": "",
    "context": "\"When standing adjacent to an ally wielding a melee weapon who is not [engaged in melee|Concept.ZoneOfControl], gain \" + getroottable().MSU.Text.colorPositive(\"+7\") + \" [Ranged Skill|Concept.RangeSkill], [Ranged Defense|Concept.RangeDefense], and [Resolve|Concept.Bravery]. The bonus increases by \" + getroottable().MSU.Text.colorPositive(\"+2\") + \" every [turn|Concept.Turn] up to a maximum of \" + getroottable().MSU.Text.colorPositive(\"+15\") + \" as long as you continue to start your [turn|Concept.Turn] adjacent to any ally wielding a melee weapon who is not [engaged in melee|Concept.ZoneOfControl].\""
  },
  {
    "key": "5cca3011211991b03ede51382746ada92d82fa306bc474be6e8bf81a69737418",
    "original": " [Reach|Concept.Reach] per adjacent ally who is wielding a two-handed weapon with a piercing attack or a shield.",
    "translation": "",
    "context": "\"When attacking or defending in melee, gain \" + getroottable().MSU.Text.colorPositive(\"+1\") + \" [Reach|Concept.Reach] per adjacent ally who is wielding a two-handed weapon with a piercing attack or a shield.\""
  },
  {
    "key": "3b27a105b07f07599629bc983b257bb080376dc1b5f030fdfbdbd3c79ad4723c",
    "original": " [Reach|Concept.Reach] while holding a [$ $|Item+throwing_net] and not currently [$ $|Skill+net_effect] a target.",
    "translation": "",
    "context": "\"Gain \" + getroottable().MSU.Text.colorPositive(\"+2\") + \" [Reach|Concept.Reach] while holding a [$ $|Item+throwing_net] and not currently [$ $|Skill+net_effect] a target.\""
  },
  {
    "key": "1978628f6d0170285addc0833baaca6da5aa0cc38386525ce93c93251c856eaf",
    "original": " [Reach|Concept.Reach].",
    "translation": "",
    "context": "\"Gain \" + getroottable().MSU.Text.colorPositive(\"+1\") + \" [Reach|Concept.Reach].\""
  },
  {
    "key": "e8d2d7d70d624dfcdf4330c0de0c3308ad997213684cfcc4eb1baa2be7951675",
    "original": " [Resolve|Concept.Bravery].",
    "translation": "",
    "context": "\"For each adjacent ally, gain \" + getroottable().MSU.Text.colorPositive(\"+2\") + \" [Melee Skill|Concept.MeleeSkill], [Ranged Skill|Concept.RangeSkill], [Melee Defense|Concept.MeleeDefense] and [Ranged Defense|Concept.RangeDefense] and \" + getroottable().MSU.Text.colorPositive(\"+5\") + \" [Resolve|Concept.Bravery].\""
  },
  {
    "key": "d7c71759cffeb4518674996466329e663289aa5dded332bb98deb29f78849aad",
    "original": " [morale checks|Concept.Morale], one for every ",
    "translation": "",
    "context": "\"This [injury|Concept.InjuryTemporary] triggers at least one additional [morale check|Concept.Morale] on the target and can trigger up to \" + getroottable().MSU.Text.colorNegative(3) + \" [morale checks|Concept.Morale], one for every \" + getroottable().MSU.Text.colorPositive(\"33%\") + \" of [Hitpoints|Concept.Hitpoints] damage dealt compared to remaining [Hitpoints|Concept.Hitpoints].\""
  },
  {
    "key": "ba0c67d85fd16ed2c283a7e3e429f6853f861479586c7db1162f6ae22fb1f02c",
    "original": " [morale|Concept.Morale].",
    "translation": "",
    "context": "\"Headshots from firearms apply the [$ $|Skill+shellshocked_effect] effect except on characters with \" + getroottable().Const.MoraleStateName[getroottable().Const.MoraleState.Ignore] + \" [morale|Concept.Morale].\""
  },
  {
    "key": "a171b89c595c9438c551e260a3d5999e951107a48ff4e02022a5269c6ed738b8",
    "original": " [talent|Concept.Talent] stars in a random attribute in which you have fewer than 3 stars.",
    "translation": "",
    "context": "\"Every time you spend a level-up, gain between \" + getroottable().MSU.Text.colorPositive(1) + \" and \" + getroottable().MSU.Text.colorPositive(3) + \" [talent|Concept.Talent] stars in a random attribute in which you have fewer than 3 stars.\""
  },
  {
    "key": "95c660a0a3432ce3ac5110b1dc0a18fc35cf54d1ace4fa1196bc26119c983b4a",
    "original": " [turn|Concept.Turn].",
    "translation": "",
    "context": "\"Any negative [status effect|Concept.StatusEffect] with a finite duration (e.g. [$ $|Skill+disarmed_effect], [$ $|Skill+charmed_effect]) has its duration reduced to \" + getroottable().MSU.Text.colorPositive(1) + \" [turn|Concept.Turn].\""
  },
  {
    "key": "e8a2964a702777aab76103a863194199332084b812295ff157f6c4d106e1bb3e",
    "original": " additional damage ignoring armor per character level.",
    "translation": "",
    "context": "\"Gain \" + getroottable().MSU.Text.colorPositive(\"+1\") + \" [Melee Skill|Concept.MeleeSkill] and [Melee Defense|Concept.MeleeDefense] and \" + getroottable().MSU.Text.colorPositive(\"+1%\") + \" additional damage ignoring armor per character level.\""
  },
  {
    "key": "fc6a6e978a977c9a2218154e9de597656195e0f4a3b25b619b9e5f9298967af0",
    "original": " after that.",
    "translation": "",
    "context": "\"[Experience|Concept.Experience] gained is increased by \" + getroottable().MSU.Text.colorPositive(\"20%\") + \" for the next 5 [levels|Concept.Level] and by \" + getroottable().MSU.Text.colorPositive(\"5%\") + \" after that.\""
  },
  {
    "key": "dba46b5af385483a1899e57d5e95cd51de3e0b3f9710aee0080a40d0af4e7dab",
    "original": " against enemies who have sustained an [injury|Concept.Injury] or are [$ $|Skill+sleeping_effect], [$ $|Skill+stunned_effect], [$ $|Skill+net_effect], [$ $|Skill+web_effect], or [$ $|Skill+rooted_effect].",
    "translation": "",
    "context": "\"Damage is increased by \" + getroottable().MSU.Text.colorPositive(\"20%\") + \" against enemies who have sustained an [injury|Concept.Injury] or are [$ $|Skill+sleeping_effect], [$ $|Skill+stunned_effect], [$ $|Skill+net_effect], [$ $|Skill+web_effect], or [$ $|Skill+rooted_effect].\""
  },
  {
    "key": "f6453c67bc98fe67283282ec2444f56c40d0fe259aebac68271aceff908c46e1",
    "original": " against negative [morale checks|Concept.Morale].",
    "translation": "",
    "context": "\"[Resolve|Concept.Bravery] is increased by \" + getroottable().MSU.Text.colorPositive(\"50%\") + \" against negative [morale checks|Concept.Morale].\""
  },
  {
    "key": "1e7721d3afd4a7557affae8d067f09664eb2ed7bc5617a229a5156d6c36b9296",
    "original": " ammo. Immediately afterward, the next throwing attack costs ",
    "translation": "",
    "context": "\"When using a throwing weapon which uses ammo, whenever you end your movement over an enemy's corpse during your [turn|Concept.Turn], recover \" + getroottable().MSU.Text.colorPositive(1) + \" ammo. Immediately afterward, the next throwing attack costs \" + getroottable().MSU.Text.colorPositive(\"no\") + \" [Action Points|Concept.ActionPoints] and builds \" + getroottable().MSU.Text.colorPositive(\"50%\") + \" less [Fatigue|Concept.Fatigue].\""
  },
  {
    "key": "e3ee915a8e8c7aa02d2fced443314522b20824abd2535d5959c41dc8ab8a09e4",
    "original": " and ",
    "translation": "",
    "context": "\"Every time you spend a level-up, gain between \" + getroottable().MSU.Text.colorPositive(1) + \" and \" + getroottable().MSU.Text.colorPositive(3) + \" [talent|Concept.Talent] stars in a random attribute in which you have fewer than 3 stars.\""
  },
  {
    "key": "e3ee915a8e8c7aa02d2fced443314522b20824abd2535d5959c41dc8ab8a09e4",
    "original": " and ",
    "translation": "",
    "context": "\"Whenever you attack or are attacked, hit or miss, gain a stacking \" + getroottable().MSU.Text.colorPositive(\"+5\") + \" [Initiative|Concept.Initiative] and \" + getroottable().MSU.Text.colorPositive(\"+5%\") + \" reduction to the [Fatigue|Concept.Fatigue] cost of skills until the end of your next [turn|Concept.Turn], up to a maximum of \" + getroottable().MSU.Text.colorPositive(\"+25\") + \" and \" + getroottable().MSU.Text.colorPositive(\"+25%\") + \" respectively.\""
  },
  {
    "key": "3650fa64cc7a1aca58a23f898d8a17b7212d4717fc18ffe414b34173a0477d45",
    "original": " and Melee Damage by ",
    "translation": "",
    "context": "\"Each stack of rage increases [Resolve|Concept.Bravery] and [Initiative|Concept.Initiative] by \" + getroottable().MSU.Text.colorPositive(\"+2\") + \" and Melee Damage by \" + getroottable().MSU.Text.colorPositive(\"2%\") + \". Each stack lowers [Melee Defense|Concept.MeleeDefense] by \" + getroottable().MSU.Text.colorNegative(\"-1\") + \" and lowers damage received by \" + getroottable().MSU.Text.colorPositive(\"2%\") + \", up to a maximum of 70%.\""
  },
  {
    "key": "d8a78f9cd3b4b924d6ca5ce5bedecda28d5dc10cb88ddac6bcedea5b7104c4e4",
    "original": " and [Initiative|Concept.Initiative] by ",
    "translation": "",
    "context": "\"Each stack increases [Action Points|Concept.ActionPoints] by \" + getroottable().MSU.Text.colorPositive(\"+1\") + \" and [Initiative|Concept.Initiative] by \" + getroottable().MSU.Text.colorPositive(\"+10\") + \".\""
  },
  {
    "key": "b1e5c473448ea62ccc3a23f9e4141d7a4ffb74c1c19111a052187fd8748bbf37",
    "original": " and lowers damage received by ",
    "translation": "",
    "context": "\"Each stack of rage increases [Resolve|Concept.Bravery] and [Initiative|Concept.Initiative] by \" + getroottable().MSU.Text.colorPositive(\"+2\") + \" and Melee Damage by \" + getroottable().MSU.Text.colorPositive(\"2%\") + \". Each stack lowers [Melee Defense|Concept.MeleeDefense] by \" + getroottable().MSU.Text.colorNegative(\"-1\") + \" and lowers damage received by \" + getroottable().MSU.Text.colorPositive(\"2%\") + \", up to a maximum of 70%.\""
  },
  {
    "key": "91e0e1aaa8ce1e5e66e0e81c27ced3e537b490c30eaabde0f3b16fa6c5d02271",
    "original": " and that to armor by ",
    "translation": "",
    "context": "\"Damage to [Hitpoints|Concept.Hitpoints] is reduced by \" + getroottable().MSU.Text.colorPositive(\"50%\") + \" and that to armor by \" + getroottable().MSU.Text.colorPositive(\"25%\") + \".\""
  },
  {
    "key": "0421a2899522313d376e5a7032fff4666f394969a8a14b367ae82c1a29d90356",
    "original": " and the [Fatigue|Concept.Fatigue] cost by ",
    "translation": "",
    "context": "\"The [Action Point|Concept.ActionPoints] costs of AOE sword skills is reduced by \" + getroottable().MSU.Text.colorPositive(2) + \" and the [Fatigue|Concept.Fatigue] cost by \" + getroottable().MSU.Text.colorPositive(\"10%\") + \".\""
  },
  {
    "key": "4e07ff2327fc5c9e3671241bcad89761f08ba25380bd6a54f4d2782b0c0699d0",
    "original": " and the attack does not build or require any [Fatigue|Concept.Fatigue].",
    "translation": "",
    "context": "\"When wielding a shield, the chance is increased by an additional \" + getroottable().MSU.Text.colorPositive(\"+15%\") + \" and the attack does not build or require any [Fatigue|Concept.Fatigue].\""
  },
  {
    "key": "6c1be2299d37a5475adc0f051a51c61e67ddb015635bdc489bba32014e4f3d16",
    "original": " and these skills build up ",
    "translation": "",
    "context": "\"When using a non-fencing sword, the [Action Point|Concept.ActionPoints] cost of non-AOE skills is reduced by \" + getroottable().MSU.Text.colorPositive(1) + \" and these skills build up \" + getroottable().MSU.Text.colorPositive(\"25%\") + \" less [Fatigue|Concept.Fatigue].\""
  },
  {
    "key": "9595ad9f535bf4234ff768d767013c03ebd68dae2857affca8bced73f448b3a8",
    "original": " and to Armor by ",
    "translation": "",
    "context": "\"Damage to [Hitpoints|Concept.Hitpoints] is reduced by \" + getroottable().MSU.Text.colorPositive(\"30%\") + \" and to Armor by \" + getroottable().MSU.Text.colorPositive(\"20%\") + \".\""
  },
  {
    "key": "6f9c35324f5dfea4a974db668df62a4c2b863cf2fb0810f7f9113ff3a29f823a",
    "original": " armor penetration and those from firearms have ",
    "translation": "",
    "context": "\"If you have not moved from your position during your [turn|Concept.Turn], ranged attacks from crossbows have \" + getroottable().MSU.Text.colorPositive(\"+10%\") + \" armor penetration and those from firearms have \" + getroottable().MSU.Text.colorPositive(\"+10%\") + \" chance to hit.\""
  },
  {
    "key": "cd7e49d908096be14a1e808573caae82d55f44c734e465ed1c609d92936e2559",
    "original": " armor penetration per character surrounding the target.",
    "translation": "",
    "context": "\"Attacks against [surrounded|Concept.Surrounding] targets deal \" + getroottable().MSU.Text.colorPositive(\"10%\") + \" more damage and have \" + getroottable().MSU.Text.colorPositive(\"+10%\") + \" armor penetration per character surrounding the target.\""
  },
  {
    "key": "6f58f0101dd5f2ceada142e6545351610536c9f9ce1c7cecf46d0ba4bd219ccd",
    "original": " armor penetration when using a bow and ",
    "translation": "",
    "context": "\"Against targets who are not in cover, gain \" + getroottable().MSU.Text.colorPositive(\"+10%\") + \" armor penetration when using a bow and \" + getroottable().MSU.Text.colorPositive(\"+20%\") + \" otherwise.\""
  },
  {
    "key": "a9ba135284025952b4f63c1c1ff347303cc56af6631617977740b76f0121605d",
    "original": " armor penetration.",
    "translation": "",
    "context": "\"Attacks have a random \" + getroottable().MSU.Text.colorPositive(\"+10%\") + \" to \" + getroottable().MSU.Text.colorPositive(\"+25%\") + \" armor penetration.\""
  },
  {
    "key": "b3bc054de473165d2ef248166ecc78cfb3aa8101c4bf36fd9c7d7595b1f1a283",
    "original": " as long as their [morale state|Concept.Morale] is lower than yours.",
    "translation": "",
    "context": "\"At the start of your [turn|Concept.Turn], if you have at least Steady [morale|Concept.Morale], improve the [morale state|Concept.Morale] of adjacent allies by \" + getroottable().MSU.Text.colorPositive(1) + \" as long as their [morale state|Concept.Morale] is lower than yours.\""
  },
  {
    "key": "ed3cc44a1d717748e97fbd7d69da95bc2945014106f77331a4065b60fe057939",
    "original": " as long as you continue to start your [turn|Concept.Turn] adjacent to any ally wielding a melee weapon who is not [engaged in melee|Concept.ZoneOfControl].",
    "translation": "",
    "context": "\"When standing adjacent to an ally wielding a melee weapon who is not [engaged in melee|Concept.ZoneOfControl], gain \" + getroottable().MSU.Text.colorPositive(\"+7\") + \" [Ranged Skill|Concept.RangeSkill], [Ranged Defense|Concept.RangeDefense], and [Resolve|Concept.Bravery]. The bonus increases by \" + getroottable().MSU.Text.colorPositive(\"+2\") + \" every [turn|Concept.Turn] up to a maximum of \" + getroottable().MSU.Text.colorPositive(\"+15\") + \" as long as you continue to start your [turn|Concept.Turn] adjacent to any ally wielding a melee weapon who is not [engaged in melee|Concept.ZoneOfControl].\""
  },
  {
    "key": "0cd7589faf641e0df15599f81524a95bab8de27a5c8bdd7dd4e5325c8909b0d9",
    "original": " at a distance of 2 tiles.",
    "translation": "",
    "context": "\"The penalty to hitchance from obstructed line of sight is reduced by \" + getroottable().MSU.Text.colorPositive(\"50%\") + \" at a distance of 2 tiles.\""
  },
  {
    "key": "48a4f5b0760822dcfb59a7c488268f5344750e400ad16427d01eafebbaa77b86",
    "original": " attacks you receive each battle.",
    "translation": "",
    "context": "\"Take reduced damage from the first \" + getroottable().MSU.Text.colorPositive(2) + \" attacks you receive each battle.\""
  },
  {
    "key": "9907f6a5ce4ec05e8072341fb8b08f98c149959ba34e2ec7f3022dcaedf103d5",
    "original": " bonus to [Melee Skill|Concept.MeleeSkill], [Ranged Skill|Concept.RangeSkill], [Melee Defense|Concept.MeleeDefense], [Ranged Defense|Concept.RangeDefense], and [Resolve|Concept.Bravery].",
    "translation": "",
    "context": "\"When no members of your faction are adjacent to you nor are there more than 1 within 2 tiles of distance from you, gain a \" + getroottable().MSU.Text.colorPositive(\"15%\") + \" bonus to [Melee Skill|Concept.MeleeSkill], [Ranged Skill|Concept.RangeSkill], [Melee Defense|Concept.MeleeDefense], [Ranged Defense|Concept.RangeDefense], and [Resolve|Concept.Bravery].\""
  },
  {
    "key": "3e2f86df191f632edf7d6729001693492cc729b19162797c4b420bc1ecf494ae",
    "original": " chance of being replaced with [$ $|Perk+perk_rf_realized_potential].",
    "translation": "",
    "context": "\"Upon reaching level 11, this perk has a \" + getroottable().MSU.Text.colorPositive(\"50%\") + \" chance of being replaced with [$ $|Perk+perk_rf_realized_potential].\""
  },
  {
    "key": "8859202ea14c638d758e762b78bde24d6f97bebe6ccd140d10d144627e95dfa9",
    "original": " chance that an enemy requires two successful rolls to hit you per negative status effect affecting the enemy. Valid status effects include: [$ $|Skill+rf_worn_down_effect], [$ $|Skill+stunned_effect], [$ $|Skill+dazed_effect], [$ $|Skill+rf_rattled_effect], [$ $|Skill+net_effect], [$ $|Skill+sleeping_effect], [$ $|Skill+staggered_effect], [$ $|Skill+rooted_effect], [$ $|Skill+web_effect].",
    "translation": "",
    "context": "\"Gain a stacking \" + getroottable().MSU.Text.colorPositive(\"20%\") + \" chance that an enemy requires two successful rolls to hit you per negative status effect affecting the enemy. Valid status effects include: [$ $|Skill+rf_worn_down_effect], [$ $|Skill+stunned_effect], [$ $|Skill+dazed_effect], [$ $|Skill+rf_rattled_effect], [$ $|Skill+net_effect], [$ $|Skill+sleeping_effect], [$ $|Skill+staggered_effect], [$ $|Skill+rooted_effect], [$ $|Skill+web_effect].\""
  },
  {
    "key": "ce72ce53223190b341bf4b5f481f9dddf2c704bebbb2ce2215a1d5f1bd911005",
    "original": " chance to [$ $|Skill+stunned_effect] the target if not immune.",
    "translation": "",
    "context": "\"[$ $|Skill+knock_out], [$ $|Skill+knock_over_skill] and [$ $|Skill+strike_down_skill] have a \" + getroottable().MSU.Text.colorPositive(\"100%\") + \" chance to [$ $|Skill+stunned_effect] the target if not immune.\""
  },
  {
    "key": "b2132c95aeffb15ec35e6c830c1af3375b2434a4679e3dda115e9b6d7db8e8ca",
    "original": " chance to apply an injury. If the attack already applied an injury, this applies an additional injury.",
    "translation": "",
    "context": "\"When attacking a target which already has at least 3 stacks of [$ $|Skill+bleeding_effect], you have a \" + getroottable().MSU.Text.colorPositive(\"33%\") + \" chance to apply an injury. If the attack already applied an injury, this applies an additional injury.\""
  },
  {
    "key": "2d01b9714f728713cfd604b885a53e06715ae1a39e30c696e96b028946cda0fa",
    "original": " chance to apply the [$ $|Skill+rf_dented_armor_effect] effect.",
    "translation": "",
    "context": "\"Successful attacks have a \" + getroottable().MSU.Text.colorPositive(\"66%\") + \" chance to apply the [$ $|Skill+rf_dented_armor_effect] effect.\""
  },
  {
    "key": "6c223e91677641342947d9d42c66f2b98cbde738f482de2a072d1cf0d077d4ff",
    "original": " chance to hit against enemies wielding ranged weapons or enemies not in cover.",
    "translation": "",
    "context": "\"Ranged attacks gain \" + getroottable().MSU.Text.colorPositive(\"+10%\") + \" chance to hit against enemies wielding ranged weapons or enemies not in cover.\""
  },
  {
    "key": "2d2a65ec0227f717e8f8ef57d9989af75c873ae4ae2f2e9afe36531398d4cd72",
    "original": " chance to hit and deal ",
    "translation": "",
    "context": "\"Melee [AOE|Concept.AOE] attacks gain \" + getroottable().MSU.Text.colorPositive(\"+10%\") + \" chance to hit and deal \" + getroottable().MSU.Text.colorPositive(\"10%\") + \" increased damage.\""
  },
  {
    "key": "2134129b478a35ea9d515c38a2e5d4d412613273103066ee27fca6016174275d",
    "original": " chance to hit or ignore the defense granted by shield, whichever is greater, and deal ",
    "translation": "",
    "context": "\"Against opponents who have missed a melee attack against you gain \" + getroottable().MSU.Text.colorPositive(\"+10%\") + \" chance to hit or ignore the defense granted by shield, whichever is greater, and deal \" + getroottable().MSU.Text.colorPositive(\"20%\") + \" more damage. Expires upon your next attack or [waiting|Concept.Wait] or ending your [turn|Concept.Turn].\""
  },
  {
    "key": "0510c26308c45832dd30d44584eb8494dc448560cc20d451881d8884b58d7428",
    "original": " chance to hit the head and ",
    "translation": "",
    "context": "\"Gain \" + getroottable().MSU.Text.colorPositive(\"+15%\") + \" chance to hit the head and \" + getroottable().MSU.Text.colorPositive(\"33%\") + \" reduced [threshold|Concept.InjuryThreshold] to inflict [injuries|Concept.InjuryTemporary] when attacking a [$ $|Skill+rf_rattled_effect], [$ $|Skill+stunned_effect], [$ $|Skill+dazed_effect], [$ $|Skill+net_effect], [$ $|Skill+sleeping_effect], [$ $|Skill+staggered_effect], [$ $|Skill+web_effect], or [$ $|Skill+rooted_effect] target.\""
  },
  {
    "key": "24cb7dfdbca69bb570b6f1308811643c7c4ca17ecda18a097150e84c7eda516e",
    "original": " chance to hit the head at a distance of 2 tiles. For every tile beyond that, this bonus is reduced by ",
    "translation": "",
    "context": "\"Gain \" + getroottable().MSU.Text.colorPositive(\"+25%\") + \" chance to hit the head at a distance of 2 tiles. For every tile beyond that, this bonus is reduced by \" + getroottable().MSU.Text.colorNegative(\"-5%\") + \".\""
  },
  {
    "key": "439f34f8e8db338d8e5971a3fc959106302b0709289fd79b97a6e63feaa9c95d",
    "original": " chance to hit the head per difference in current [Reach|Concept.Reach] between you and the target.",
    "translation": "",
    "context": "\"With two-handed flails, when attacking a target who has lower current [Reach|Concept.Reach] than you, gain \" + getroottable().MSU.Text.colorPositive(\"+10%\") + \" chance to hit the head per difference in current [Reach|Concept.Reach] between you and the target.\""
  },
  {
    "key": "de3a84eef91eec789471c9034b421f5196e41552ed21de36e38a3df96a97c9bb",
    "original": " chance to hit the head.",
    "translation": "",
    "context": "\"When attacking a target at a range of 2 tiles, gain \" + getroottable().MSU.Text.colorNegative(\"+20%\") + \" chance to hit the head.\""
  },
  {
    "key": "de3a84eef91eec789471c9034b421f5196e41552ed21de36e38a3df96a97c9bb",
    "original": " chance to hit the head.",
    "translation": "",
    "context": "\"All attacks, melee or ranged, gain \" + getroottable().MSU.Text.colorPositive(\"+10%\") + \" chance to hit the head.\""
  },
  {
    "key": "de3a84eef91eec789471c9034b421f5196e41552ed21de36e38a3df96a97c9bb",
    "original": " chance to hit the head.",
    "translation": "",
    "context": "\"Attacks have an additional \" + getroottable().MSU.Text.colorPositive(\"25%\") + \" chance to hit the head.\""
  },
  {
    "key": "c625d76db815a3f8cc054d108f1f74576101544b3238700c54e13a807ba188da",
    "original": " chance to hit their partner and inflict ",
    "translation": "",
    "context": "\"A partner's melee [AOE|Concept.AOE] attacks never have more than \" + getroottable().MSU.Text.colorPositive(getroottable().Const.Combat.MV_HitChanceMin + \"%\") + \" chance to hit their partner and inflict \" + getroottable().MSU.Text.colorPositive(\"50%\") + \" less damage.\""
  },
  {
    "key": "dac4049ba9dfb460009b085507752ed41cc8a332dfa670f666c0f2d7a426f3df",
    "original": " chance to hit.",
    "translation": "",
    "context": "\"[$ $|Skill+thresh] gains \" + getroottable().MSU.Text.colorPositive(\"+5%\") + \" chance to hit.\""
  },
  {
    "key": "dac4049ba9dfb460009b085507752ed41cc8a332dfa670f666c0f2d7a426f3df",
    "original": " chance to hit.",
    "translation": "",
    "context": "\"Skills build up \" + getroottable().MSU.Text.colorPositive(\"20%\") + \" less [Fatigue|Concept.Fatigue] and gain \" + getroottable().MSU.Text.colorPositive(\"+10%\") + \" chance to hit.\""
  },
  {
    "key": "dac4049ba9dfb460009b085507752ed41cc8a332dfa670f666c0f2d7a426f3df",
    "original": " chance to hit.",
    "translation": "",
    "context": "\"[$ $|Skill+split] and [$ $|Skill+swing] no longer have a penalty to hitchance and gain \" + getroottable().MSU.Text.colorPositive(\"+5%\") + \" chance to hit.\""
  },
  {
    "key": "dac4049ba9dfb460009b085507752ed41cc8a332dfa670f666c0f2d7a426f3df",
    "original": " chance to hit.",
    "translation": "",
    "context": "\"If you have not moved from your position during your [turn|Concept.Turn], ranged attacks from crossbows have \" + getroottable().MSU.Text.colorPositive(\"+10%\") + \" armor penetration and those from firearms have \" + getroottable().MSU.Text.colorPositive(\"+10%\") + \" chance to hit.\""
  },
  {
    "key": "dac4049ba9dfb460009b085507752ed41cc8a332dfa670f666c0f2d7a426f3df",
    "original": " chance to hit.",
    "translation": "",
    "context": "\"[$ $|Skill+knock_back] gains \" + getroottable().MSU.Text.colorPositive(\"+15%\") + \" chance to hit.\""
  },
  {
    "key": "dac4049ba9dfb460009b085507752ed41cc8a332dfa670f666c0f2d7a426f3df",
    "original": " chance to hit.",
    "translation": "",
    "context": "\"[$ $|Skill+round_swing] gains \" + getroottable().MSU.Text.colorPositive(\"+5%\") + \" chance to hit.\""
  },
  {
    "key": "dac4049ba9dfb460009b085507752ed41cc8a332dfa670f666c0f2d7a426f3df",
    "original": " chance to hit.",
    "translation": "",
    "context": "\"[$ $|Skill+shatter_skill] gains \" + getroottable().MSU.Text.colorPositive(\"+5%\") + \" chance to hit.\""
  },
  {
    "key": "9ca4758288030993ae66e8da30448606c4dc3dad5a172a7c21d6384d5df87bff",
    "original": " chance to inflict [$ $|Skill+staggered_effect] and if the target is already [$ $|Skill+staggered_effect], ",
    "translation": "",
    "context": "\"Hits from throwing attacks now apply certain debuffs on the target. Piercing type attacks have a \" + getroottable().MSU.Text.colorPositive(\"50%\") + \" chance to inflict the [$ $|Skill+rf_arrow_to_the_knee_debuff_effect] effect. Cutting type attacks always apply the [$ $|Skill+overwhelmed_effect] effect. Blunt type attacks have a \" + getroottable().MSU.Text.colorPositive(\"50%\") + \" chance to inflict [$ $|Skill+staggered_effect] and if the target is already [$ $|Skill+staggered_effect], \" + getroottable().MSU.Text.colorPositive(\"100%\") + \" chance to inflict [$ $|Skill+stunned_effect].\""
  },
  {
    "key": "5062ed3e9b416c8405df85ab7b5699baecc67b1e861c250e51848097aaf7503e",
    "original": " chance to inflict [$ $|Skill+stunned_effect].",
    "translation": "",
    "context": "\"Hits from throwing attacks now apply certain debuffs on the target. Piercing type attacks have a \" + getroottable().MSU.Text.colorPositive(\"50%\") + \" chance to inflict the [$ $|Skill+rf_arrow_to_the_knee_debuff_effect] effect. Cutting type attacks always apply the [$ $|Skill+overwhelmed_effect] effect. Blunt type attacks have a \" + getroottable().MSU.Text.colorPositive(\"50%\") + \" chance to inflict [$ $|Skill+staggered_effect] and if the target is already [$ $|Skill+staggered_effect], \" + getroottable().MSU.Text.colorPositive(\"100%\") + \" chance to inflict [$ $|Skill+stunned_effect].\""
  },
  {
    "key": "b61fbbc5d387debf2c818bd0e1f3551cc11637fb15df9c68a7915333dfe4c281",
    "original": " chance to inflict the [$ $|Skill+rf_arrow_to_the_knee_debuff_effect] effect. Cutting type attacks always apply the [$ $|Skill+overwhelmed_effect] effect. Blunt type attacks have a ",
    "translation": "",
    "context": "\"Hits from throwing attacks now apply certain debuffs on the target. Piercing type attacks have a \" + getroottable().MSU.Text.colorPositive(\"50%\") + \" chance to inflict the [$ $|Skill+rf_arrow_to_the_knee_debuff_effect] effect. Cutting type attacks always apply the [$ $|Skill+overwhelmed_effect] effect. Blunt type attacks have a \" + getroottable().MSU.Text.colorPositive(\"50%\") + \" chance to inflict [$ $|Skill+staggered_effect] and if the target is already [$ $|Skill+staggered_effect], \" + getroottable().MSU.Text.colorPositive(\"100%\") + \" chance to inflict [$ $|Skill+stunned_effect].\""
  },
  {
    "key": "531d38da3ddd94141675fd89feff6424fa023f4ffe77ea38c8623bef36001864",
    "original": " chance to perform a free extra attack of the same type with ",
    "translation": "",
    "context": "\"During your turn, attacks have a \" + getroottable().MSU.Text.colorPositive(\"50%\") + \" chance to perform a free extra attack of the same type with \" + getroottable().MSU.Text.colorNegative(\"50%\") + \" reduced damage.\""
  },
  {
    "key": "6f0aacb6213c41c9754f73f0b55481b6e474fd0b8fe869ea870bcdd2f5006b68",
    "original": " chance to perform an attack against an adjacent opponent who misses a melee attack against you. This attack costs no [Action Points|Concept.ActionPoints] but can only trigger if you have enough [Fatigue|Concept.Fatigue] to afford it. A resolve check is triggered for you, and if successful, the attack builds no [Fatigue|Concept.Fatigue].",
    "translation": "",
    "context": "\"Gain a \" + getroottable().MSU.Text.colorPositive(\"25%\") + \" chance to perform an attack against an adjacent opponent who misses a melee attack against you. This attack costs no [Action Points|Concept.ActionPoints] but can only trigger if you have enough [Fatigue|Concept.Fatigue] to afford it. A resolve check is triggered for you, and if successful, the attack builds no [Fatigue|Concept.Fatigue].\""
  },
  {
    "key": "193651623859c8c5b94e9f81b97e19c940284a1bc4c1f392d5cb8a6dd60713cf",
    "original": " chance to succeed.",
    "translation": "",
    "context": "\"A [$ $|Skill+player_character_trait] has a \" + getroottable().MSU.Text.colorPositive(\"100%\") + \" chance to succeed.\""
  },
  {
    "key": "db6dbfc9647be9c0561e5c5309b985d7b785e68e16e70f3bff1c4c0c2ce1ad09",
    "original": " costs no [Action Points|Concept.ActionPoints].",
    "translation": "",
    "context": "\"Once per [turn|Concept.Turn], the first use of your offhand item weighing less than \" + getroottable().MSU.Text.colorNegative(10) + \" costs no [Action Points|Concept.ActionPoints].\""
  },
  {
    "key": "8f8e4f456304b91386c9cb813e2b0f98a288b60d19938188a90bf71ae13b35fa",
    "original": " damage bonus for your next attack.",
    "translation": "",
    "context": "\"Every time you are hit, gain a stacking \" + getroottable().MSU.Text.colorPositive(\"25%\") + \" damage bonus for your next attack.\""
  },
  {
    "key": "014029c757ee55331033310a2a47fb485433c63e289c8a076d1b90d6a3ffd168",
    "original": " damage ignoring armor. This bonus expires upon taking any action other than an attack.",
    "translation": "",
    "context": "\"When wielding a melee weapon with up to 4 [Reach|Concept.Reach] and ending your movement next to a [surrounded|Concept.Surrounding] enemy, the next attack against that enemy deals \" + getroottable().MSU.Text.colorPositive(\"25%\") + \" more damage and \" + getroottable().MSU.Text.colorPositive(\"+20%\") + \" damage ignoring armor. This bonus expires upon taking any action other than an attack.\""
  },
  {
    "key": "2bdf37a39dc394ca4e07229d1237d1a235f8410e2b5f95fbf661c51a28f74753",
    "original": " damage received ignoring armor on the body part hit for the remainder of the combat.",
    "translation": "",
    "context": "\"Every successful hit has a chance to apply the [$ $|Skill+rf_dismantled_effect] effect, which causes the target to receive a stacking \" + getroottable().MSU.Text.colorNegative(\"+20%\") + \" damage received ignoring armor on the body part hit for the remainder of the combat.\""
  },
  {
    "key": "b679030a8fdf6d002da415e2d20b6fb05262ac67e0d389c2602de3e3e8b8b29c",
    "original": " damage to [Hitpoints|Concept.Hitpoints] and apply a valid [status effect|Concept.StatusEffect] or are against characters with a valid [status effect|Concept.StatusEffect] have a chance to inflict an [injury|Concept.Injury]. This chance is ",
    "translation": "",
    "context": "\"Attacks that do at least \" + getroottable().MSU.Text.colorNegative(5) + \" damage to [Hitpoints|Concept.Hitpoints] and apply a valid [status effect|Concept.StatusEffect] or are against characters with a valid [status effect|Concept.StatusEffect] have a chance to inflict an [injury|Concept.Injury]. This chance is \" + getroottable().MSU.Text.colorPositive(\"100%\") + \" for two-handed maces and \" + getroottable().MSU.Text.colorPositive(\"50%\") + \" for one-handed maces.\""
  },
  {
    "key": "f9cf29d37819e831190eb3cffb81347ec0fe59ff8b9b84d7b82fc77ecd6f6134",
    "original": " during [morale checks|Concept.Morale].",
    "translation": "",
    "context": "\"Lower the [Resolve|Concept.Bravery] of adjacent enemies by \" + getroottable().MSU.Text.colorNegative(\"-10\") + \" during [morale checks|Concept.Morale].\""
  },
  {
    "key": "30da0a0a2d7c1241795dfd75af2b7d4895c45981fc878566758f358c08f48877",
    "original": " every [turn|Concept.Turn] up to a maximum of ",
    "translation": "",
    "context": "\"When standing adjacent to an ally wielding a melee weapon who is not [engaged in melee|Concept.ZoneOfControl], gain \" + getroottable().MSU.Text.colorPositive(\"+7\") + \" [Ranged Skill|Concept.RangeSkill], [Ranged Defense|Concept.RangeDefense], and [Resolve|Concept.Bravery]. The bonus increases by \" + getroottable().MSU.Text.colorPositive(\"+2\") + \" every [turn|Concept.Turn] up to a maximum of \" + getroottable().MSU.Text.colorPositive(\"+15\") + \" as long as you continue to start your [turn|Concept.Turn] adjacent to any ally wielding a melee weapon who is not [engaged in melee|Concept.ZoneOfControl].\""
  },
  {
    "key": "f6ff45d3c7bf9dcc0f05d2dc568084daad10e1f0d2319ddaad0547a8be110d1a",
    "original": " experience from battle.",
    "translation": "",
    "context": "\"Gain additional \" + getroottable().MSU.Text.colorPositive(\"20%\") + \" experience from battle.\""
  },
  {
    "key": "7a18cd1e4de49247900be2d52f7ba375c11512d5bf501aa16736bd6f264987ef",
    "original": " fewer [Action Points|Concept.ActionPoints] and builds ",
    "translation": "",
    "context": "\"[$ $|Skill+rf_passing_step_skill] costs \" + getroottable().MSU.Text.colorPositive(2) + \" fewer [Action Points|Concept.ActionPoints] and builds \" + getroottable().MSU.Text.colorPositive(2) + \" less [Fatigue|Concept.Fatigue], both down to a minimum of 0.\""
  },
  {
    "key": "3566b1effe0603a0ac441ac1315b6782b8689c25640550f41b33d6cb62db7fe7",
    "original": " for both melee and ranged attacks.",
    "translation": "",
    "context": "\"Lowers the [threshold|Concept.InjuryThreshold] to inflict [injuries|Concept.Injury] by \" + getroottable().MSU.Text.colorNegative(\"33%\") + \" for both melee and ranged attacks.\""
  },
  {
    "key": "2db2028dad42e70db9de3561316f3777718380d6a1d2520af20a993fa87f6ab4",
    "original": " for each tile between the attacker and you.",
    "translation": "",
    "context": "\"This reduction is a percentage equal to your current [Ranged Defense|Concept.RangeDefense] plus an additional \" + getroottable().MSU.Text.colorPositive(\"10%\") + \" for each tile between the attacker and you.\""
  },
  {
    "key": "ace0d5ea013263762baa8b8d34cbe6f92863109601bfe525243c7a780f643fa1",
    "original": " for one [turn|Concept.Turn].",
    "translation": "",
    "context": "\"With every attack, hit or miss, against an opponent that acts after you in the current round, inflict the [$ $|Skill+overwhelmed_effect] status effect which lowers both [Melee Skill|Concept.MeleeSkill] and [Ranged Skill|Concept.RangeSkill] by \" + getroottable().MSU.Text.colorNegative(\"-10%\") + \" for one [turn|Concept.Turn].\""
  },
  {
    "key": "ace0d5ea013263762baa8b8d34cbe6f92863109601bfe525243c7a780f643fa1",
    "original": " for one [turn|Concept.Turn].",
    "translation": "",
    "context": "\"Successful hits from Flails progressively reduce the target's [Melee Defense|Concept.MeleeDefense] and [Ranged Defense|Concept.RangeDefense] by a stacking \" + getroottable().MSU.Text.colorNegative(-5) + \" for one [turn|Concept.Turn].\""
  },
  {
    "key": "c015fe3589e7f351707782dff47914abbffdae3c69713628329308241e900cf1",
    "original": " for one-handed maces.",
    "translation": "",
    "context": "\"Attacks that do at least \" + getroottable().MSU.Text.colorNegative(5) + \" damage to [Hitpoints|Concept.Hitpoints] and apply a valid [status effect|Concept.StatusEffect] or are against characters with a valid [status effect|Concept.StatusEffect] have a chance to inflict an [injury|Concept.Injury]. This chance is \" + getroottable().MSU.Text.colorPositive(\"100%\") + \" for two-handed maces and \" + getroottable().MSU.Text.colorPositive(\"50%\") + \" for one-handed maces.\""
  },
  {
    "key": "c07bcab5dae8755ffc2363ea3810e13e5f8239953d0c0fc87d6c979bbc857780",
    "original": " for one-handed weapon with shield, and ",
    "translation": "",
    "context": "\"Additional damage ignores armor. This bonus is \" + getroottable().MSU.Text.colorPositive(\"25%\") + \" for one-handed weapons, \" + getroottable().MSU.Text.colorPositive(\"35%\") + \" for one-handed weapon with shield, and \" + getroottable().MSU.Text.colorPositive(\"15%\") + \" for two-handed weapons.\""
  },
  {
    "key": "2d598cb35af7a1cd4328df8a30ad41b2b90abcea84684f2c80e7c5f8a028eaa9",
    "original": " for one-handed weapons, ",
    "translation": "",
    "context": "\"Additional damage ignores armor. This bonus is \" + getroottable().MSU.Text.colorPositive(\"25%\") + \" for one-handed weapons, \" + getroottable().MSU.Text.colorPositive(\"35%\") + \" for one-handed weapon with shield, and \" + getroottable().MSU.Text.colorPositive(\"15%\") + \" for two-handed weapons.\""
  },
  {
    "key": "0a606c72bd7964c4538f21515a9261dd7107c2582518d7557fa71315da47b096",
    "original": " for returning a missed attack. The attacks triggered from this [$ $|Perk+perk_rf_rebuke] do not build [Fatigue|Concept.Fatigue].",
    "translation": "",
    "context": "\"Use [$ $|Skill+riposte] for free at the end of your [turn|Concept.Turn] if you have access to [$ $|Skill+riposte]. Otherwise, gain [$ $|Perk+perk_rf_rebuke] instead for one [turn|Concept.Turn], with an additional chance of \" + getroottable().MSU.Text.colorPositive(\"+15%\") + \" for returning a missed attack. The attacks triggered from this [$ $|Perk+perk_rf_rebuke] do not build [Fatigue|Concept.Fatigue].\""
  },
  {
    "key": "1c0490914c920e6a0c251c5c0387a8f5d910c5b3c78cdc99459d47c41b8cc479",
    "original": " for the next 5 [levels|Concept.Level] and by ",
    "translation": "",
    "context": "\"[Experience|Concept.Experience] gained is increased by \" + getroottable().MSU.Text.colorPositive(\"20%\") + \" for the next 5 [levels|Concept.Level] and by \" + getroottable().MSU.Text.colorPositive(\"5%\") + \" after that.\""
  },
  {
    "key": "00487b6ff473fa6ec6cac3c1941c917109bc7fb3f387e6623a1cbff6260b74a7",
    "original": " for the remainder of this [turn|Concept.Turn].",
    "translation": "",
    "context": "\"A successful attack with your mainhand dagger reduces the [Action Point|Concept.ActionPoints] cost of all its skills by \" + getroottable().MSU.Text.colorPositive(\"2\") + \" to a minimum of \" + getroottable().MSU.Text.colorPositive(\"2\") + \" for the remainder of this [turn|Concept.Turn].\""
  },
  {
    "key": "82fc1ede0928af3a280f2486357786b22b20fd476a0e398d36b0d1e64eb45d49",
    "original": " for their attacks against you.",
    "translation": "",
    "context": "\"AOE attacks, hit or miss, increase your [Reach|Concept.Reach] by \" + getroottable().MSU.Text.colorPositive(\"+3\") + \". Additionally, the targeted enemies' [Reach|Concept.Reach] is reduced by \" + getroottable().MSU.Text.colorPositive(\"-3\") + \" for their attacks against you.\""
  },
  {
    "key": "f7e3ceaa29d188bd5c935fb201a0a82b690814dd39bcb84f4d659526cf0ba1c8",
    "original": " for two-handed maces and ",
    "translation": "",
    "context": "\"Attacks that do at least \" + getroottable().MSU.Text.colorNegative(5) + \" damage to [Hitpoints|Concept.Hitpoints] and apply a valid [status effect|Concept.StatusEffect] or are against characters with a valid [status effect|Concept.StatusEffect] have a chance to inflict an [injury|Concept.Injury]. This chance is \" + getroottable().MSU.Text.colorPositive(\"100%\") + \" for two-handed maces and \" + getroottable().MSU.Text.colorPositive(\"50%\") + \" for one-handed maces.\""
  },
  {
    "key": "fc797baaddff3c1f91cac159415f713fb70b196e8679ced8272715bf5fe3eb00",
    "original": " for two-handed weapons.",
    "translation": "",
    "context": "\"Additional damage ignores armor. This bonus is \" + getroottable().MSU.Text.colorPositive(\"25%\") + \" for one-handed weapons, \" + getroottable().MSU.Text.colorPositive(\"35%\") + \" for one-handed weapon with shield, and \" + getroottable().MSU.Text.colorPositive(\"15%\") + \" for two-handed weapons.\""
  },
  {
    "key": "d70055a195955b6181f6b76d0dcd4be4338729ca9c14cee4e55bfc452d3be1e2",
    "original": " have their [Action Point|Concept.ActionPoints] cost reduced to ",
    "translation": "",
    "context": "\"All skills with two-handed weapons, with a range of 2 tiles, having an [Action Point|Concept.ActionPoints] cost of \" + getroottable().MSU.Text.colorNegative(\"6\") + \" have their [Action Point|Concept.ActionPoints] cost reduced to \" + getroottable().MSU.Text.colorNegative(\"5\") + \".\""
  },
  {
    "key": "8a076fd88885f2656b2dbbd6acdceb301b6a2422a73abaf9fbbd835de71c7dea",
    "original": " if your [Initiative|Concept.Initiative] is greater than that of your target.",
    "translation": "",
    "context": "\"When attacking a target against whom you have a [Reach Disadvantage|Concept.ReachAdvantage], reduce this disadvantage by \" + getroottable().MSU.Text.colorPositive(1) + \" if your [Initiative|Concept.Initiative] is greater than that of your target.\""
  },
  {
    "key": "660d9c87f10903e7c2b4f29325e8840de5caa35bf90e9f3b100e32b50097dcdc",
    "original": " increased [Action Point|Concept.ActionPoints] cost for using the [$ $|Skill+break_free_skill] skill.",
    "translation": "",
    "context": "\"Enemies [$ $|Skill+net_effect] by you at a distance of 2 or fewer tiles have a \" + getroottable().MSU.Text.colorNegative(\"50%\") + \" increased [Action Point|Concept.ActionPoints] cost for using the [$ $|Skill+break_free_skill] skill.\""
  },
  {
    "key": "186dc6098226fadf0f9da7bf3ab2d8216d84bc439e84b82faa110b8b3f4bea20",
    "original": " increased damage for the remainder of the combat.",
    "translation": "",
    "context": "\"Whenever an ally dies adjacent to you, gain a stacking \" + getroottable().MSU.Text.colorPositive(\"5%\") + \" increased damage for the remainder of the combat.\""
  },
  {
    "key": "4fde54a41b1a9b36939399d8d25a90a37d90aeb83ff2f14da58aeea0ba4581ac",
    "original": " increased damage.",
    "translation": "",
    "context": "\"Melee [AOE|Concept.AOE] attacks gain \" + getroottable().MSU.Text.colorPositive(\"+10%\") + \" chance to hit and deal \" + getroottable().MSU.Text.colorPositive(\"10%\") + \" increased damage.\""
  },
  {
    "key": "bcf81cd7f84262b9d1fea264079a6805249950c215b35caada199e5cb5396dd5",
    "original": " less [Fatigue|Concept.Fatigue] and gain ",
    "translation": "",
    "context": "\"Skills build up \" + getroottable().MSU.Text.colorPositive(\"20%\") + \" less [Fatigue|Concept.Fatigue] and gain \" + getroottable().MSU.Text.colorPositive(\"+10%\") + \" chance to hit.\""
  },
  {
    "key": "28c7ca66bd261f717fd24c308a0f2f47a4b02fcfa73acba09c61db5658c0ec6d",
    "original": " less [Fatigue|Concept.Fatigue] per such stack.",
    "translation": "",
    "context": "\"During a [turn|Concept.Turn] gain \" + getroottable().MSU.Text.colorPositive(\"half\") + \" of the stacks gained during the previous [turn|Concept.Turn] as additional [Action Points|Concept.ActionPoints] and attacks build up \" + getroottable().MSU.Text.colorPositive(\"5%\") + \" less [Fatigue|Concept.Fatigue] per such stack.\""
  },
  {
    "key": "edf775f1a32295a8034adc112a2ccd6c4fc10a71bccd0311e548cdfa2988c517",
    "original": " less [Fatigue|Concept.Fatigue] while you have at least 2 stacks.",
    "translation": "",
    "context": "\"Skills build up \" + getroottable().MSU.Text.colorPositive(\"15%\") + \" less [Fatigue|Concept.Fatigue] while you have at least 2 stacks.\""
  },
  {
    "key": "eabef4ec97e7f1850ef9165fcb1429e0da57a87ca8980a92f291cc3c6921db1a",
    "original": " less [Fatigue|Concept.Fatigue], both down to a minimum of 0.",
    "translation": "",
    "context": "\"[$ $|Skill+rf_passing_step_skill] costs \" + getroottable().MSU.Text.colorPositive(2) + \" fewer [Action Points|Concept.ActionPoints] and builds \" + getroottable().MSU.Text.colorPositive(2) + \" less [Fatigue|Concept.Fatigue], both down to a minimum of 0.\""
  },
  {
    "key": "8367914b98196540bda6dee4f290cc765cf948090b3d004491a1a0b5d17d5127",
    "original": " less [Fatigue|Concept.Fatigue].",
    "translation": "",
    "context": "\"Skills build up \" + getroottable().MSU.Text.colorPositive(\"25%\") + \" less [Fatigue|Concept.Fatigue].\""
  },
  {
    "key": "8367914b98196540bda6dee4f290cc765cf948090b3d004491a1a0b5d17d5127",
    "original": " less [Fatigue|Concept.Fatigue].",
    "translation": "",
    "context": "\"When using a throwing weapon which uses ammo, whenever you end your movement over an enemy's corpse during your [turn|Concept.Turn], recover \" + getroottable().MSU.Text.colorPositive(1) + \" ammo. Immediately afterward, the next throwing attack costs \" + getroottable().MSU.Text.colorPositive(\"no\") + \" [Action Points|Concept.ActionPoints] and builds \" + getroottable().MSU.Text.colorPositive(\"50%\") + \" less [Fatigue|Concept.Fatigue].\""
  },
  {
    "key": "8367914b98196540bda6dee4f290cc765cf948090b3d004491a1a0b5d17d5127",
    "original": " less [Fatigue|Concept.Fatigue].",
    "translation": "",
    "context": "\"When using a non-fencing sword, the [Action Point|Concept.ActionPoints] cost of non-AOE skills is reduced by \" + getroottable().MSU.Text.colorPositive(1) + \" and these skills build up \" + getroottable().MSU.Text.colorPositive(\"25%\") + \" less [Fatigue|Concept.Fatigue].\""
  },
  {
    "key": "440ddc4b6e9d31e5c33c3e3c06ae118b186e7b6fd3eb47f52d04b919da3156cf",
    "original": " less [Fatigue|Concept.Fatigue]. This expires upon moving from your position if using a two-handed spear, or moving more than 1 tile if using a one-handed spear.",
    "translation": "",
    "context": "\"When starting your [turn|Concept.Turn] with a spear equipped, the first piercing spear attack costs \" + getroottable().MSU.Text.colorPositive(\"no\") + \" [Action Points|Concept.ActionPoints] and builds \" + getroottable().MSU.Text.colorPositive(\"50%\") + \" less [Fatigue|Concept.Fatigue]. This expires upon moving from your position if using a two-handed spear, or moving more than 1 tile if using a one-handed spear.\""
  },
  {
    "key": "3e413e611837f5369136ff7625f51505ae9b8eb7aa14f35122208d94bbd28445",
    "original": " less damage against a different adjacent enemy who has lower current [Reach|Concept.Reach] than you. This extra attack does not increase your [Reach|Concept.Reach].",
    "translation": "",
    "context": "\"During your [turn|Concept.Turn], when attacking with one-handed flails, perform a free extra attack with \" + getroottable().MSU.Text.colorNegative(\"50%\") + \" less damage against a different adjacent enemy who has lower current [Reach|Concept.Reach] than you. This extra attack does not increase your [Reach|Concept.Reach].\""
  },
  {
    "key": "69014b4e1a4d6436cd872aa4d9696f18a887498399005931f2510432b9c59024",
    "original": " less damage.",
    "translation": "",
    "context": "\"A partner's melee [AOE|Concept.AOE] attacks never have more than \" + getroottable().MSU.Text.colorPositive(getroottable().Const.Combat.MV_HitChanceMin + \"%\") + \" chance to hit their partner and inflict \" + getroottable().MSU.Text.colorPositive(\"50%\") + \" less damage.\""
  },
  {
    "key": "7d9a7e79c95050a0fc84acb72a6dd5940c3d01b2ca5d0325b1ecb839d061c125",
    "original": " lower [threshold|Concept.InjuryThreshold] to inflict [injuries|Concept.InjuryTemporary].",
    "translation": "",
    "context": "\"[$ $|Skill+gash_skill] has a \" + getroottable().MSU.Text.colorNegative(\"50%\") + \" lower [threshold|Concept.InjuryThreshold] to inflict [injuries|Concept.InjuryTemporary].\""
  },
  {
    "key": "7d9a7e79c95050a0fc84acb72a6dd5940c3d01b2ca5d0325b1ecb839d061c125",
    "original": " lower [threshold|Concept.InjuryThreshold] to inflict [injuries|Concept.InjuryTemporary].",
    "translation": "",
    "context": "\"[$ $|Skill+rf_gouge_skill] has a \" + getroottable().MSU.Text.colorNegative(\"50%\") + \" lower [threshold|Concept.InjuryThreshold] to inflict [injuries|Concept.InjuryTemporary].\""
  },
  {
    "key": "830b90f5aad4384b54f3446c1cee25a85a15a1c6b9ac0427f3735aa78fd2eead",
    "original": " more [Fatigue|Concept.Fatigue].",
    "translation": "",
    "context": "\"Each subsequent [$ $|Skill+quick_shot] in a [turn|Concept.Turn] builds \" + getroottable().MSU.Text.colorNegative(\"10%\") + \" more [Fatigue|Concept.Fatigue].\""
  },
  {
    "key": "00d2646a387d8554ae5aaed2cce876a0ce2bb7f39ae53bc5312cc7a076c44e33",
    "original": " more daily wage.",
    "translation": "",
    "context": "\"Require \" + getroottable().MSU.Text.colorNegative(\"100%\") + \" more daily wage.\""
  },
  {
    "key": "cfc2c0a58f3f71828a1e58ea240d22f34a5459159b7f03c4a336a5930059006d",
    "original": " more damage against anyone who has not started their [turn|Concept.Turn] yet in the current [round|Concept.Round].",
    "translation": "",
    "context": "\"Deal \" + getroottable().MSU.Text.colorPositive(\"20%\") + \" more damage against anyone who has not started their [turn|Concept.Turn] yet in the current [round|Concept.Round].\""
  },
  {
    "key": "ca4083553bb9b6af70905349a015af4a8ead9f144e5e2b35db57276437dcf7ec",
    "original": " more damage against armor and apply the [$ $|Skill+rf_dented_armor_effect] effect.",
    "translation": "",
    "context": "\"[$ $|Skill+crush_armor] and [$ $|Skill+demolish_armor_skill] inflict \" + getroottable().MSU.Text.colorPositive(\"33%\") + \" more damage against armor and apply the [$ $|Skill+rf_dented_armor_effect] effect.\""
  },
  {
    "key": "3953e69246ab49a30cecfc920da97dd6e4c937ebc219ce9127ceb473c017d864",
    "original": " more damage and ",
    "translation": "",
    "context": "\"When wielding a melee weapon with up to 4 [Reach|Concept.Reach] and ending your movement next to a [surrounded|Concept.Surrounding] enemy, the next attack against that enemy deals \" + getroottable().MSU.Text.colorPositive(\"25%\") + \" more damage and \" + getroottable().MSU.Text.colorPositive(\"+20%\") + \" damage ignoring armor. This bonus expires upon taking any action other than an attack.\""
  },
  {
    "key": "111bcee3f2edd29d00a317f8268d047611face10bc0de3916abd8ecf0bc9052d",
    "original": " more damage and have ",
    "translation": "",
    "context": "\"Attacks against [surrounded|Concept.Surrounding] targets deal \" + getroottable().MSU.Text.colorPositive(\"10%\") + \" more damage and have \" + getroottable().MSU.Text.colorPositive(\"+10%\") + \" armor penetration per character surrounding the target.\""
  },
  {
    "key": "395a7a3ddb2c60bafd7bdd8ad987727742333e79a02105ea916cc42f8b778702",
    "original": " more damage per level of [morale|Concept.Morale] difference.",
    "translation": "",
    "context": "\"Attacks against characters with a lower [morale|Concept.Morale] than you deal \" + getroottable().MSU.Text.colorPositive(\"10%\") + \" more damage per level of [morale|Concept.Morale] difference.\""
  },
  {
    "key": "c3e07fdaf55b1346466440eb74a2eb5dcece989727d6fb6f06e21a949cde9ac5",
    "original": " more damage while you have 3 stacks.",
    "translation": "",
    "context": "\"Deal \" + getroottable().MSU.Text.colorPositive(\"15%\") + \" more damage while you have 3 stacks.\""
  },
  {
    "key": "3248609d5281ed4101e526e4f2a7d32378a30da56877e84a67dcbd4be01a0e3b",
    "original": " more damage. Expires upon your next attack or [waiting|Concept.Wait] or ending your [turn|Concept.Turn].",
    "translation": "",
    "context": "\"Against opponents who have missed a melee attack against you gain \" + getroottable().MSU.Text.colorPositive(\"+10%\") + \" chance to hit or ignore the defense granted by shield, whichever is greater, and deal \" + getroottable().MSU.Text.colorPositive(\"20%\") + \" more damage. Expires upon your next attack or [waiting|Concept.Wait] or ending your [turn|Concept.Turn].\""
  },
  {
    "key": "6da2880e686eb5459ee0c5a59758cbeaf9e1b31f72b2a0378415c2d05e95b187",
    "original": " of [Base|Concept.BaseAttribute] [Maximum Fatigue|Concept.MaximumFatigue].",
    "translation": "",
    "context": "\"Once per [turn|Concept.Turn], killing an opponent reduces current [Fatigue|Concept.Fatigue] by \" + getroottable().MSU.Text.colorPositive(\"10%\") + \" of [Base|Concept.BaseAttribute] [Maximum Fatigue|Concept.MaximumFatigue].\""
  },
  {
    "key": "36dcccef9562e83165a16bccc7a5fdf6c40f2205a929491eb9f383367c1263b6",
    "original": " of [Hitpoints|Concept.Hitpoints] damage dealt compared to remaining [Hitpoints|Concept.Hitpoints].",
    "translation": "",
    "context": "\"This [injury|Concept.InjuryTemporary] triggers at least one additional [morale check|Concept.Morale] on the target and can trigger up to \" + getroottable().MSU.Text.colorNegative(3) + \" [morale checks|Concept.Morale], one for every \" + getroottable().MSU.Text.colorPositive(\"33%\") + \" of [Hitpoints|Concept.Hitpoints] damage dealt compared to remaining [Hitpoints|Concept.Hitpoints].\""
  },
  {
    "key": "c8c77e4d226d1e17d7c62aad412d217698cc0c2c0646bc7c092db7bb93b4087f",
    "original": " of accumulated [Fatigue|Concept.Fatigue], instead of all of it.",
    "translation": "",
    "context": "\"At all times your [Initiative|Concept.Initiative] is reduced only by \" + getroottable().MSU.Text.colorPositive(\"50%\") + \" of accumulated [Fatigue|Concept.Fatigue], instead of all of it.\""
  },
  {
    "key": "cbb2e59e6b4287a40f04ff4f48675a164de0562ef574a435a62c24fe209d1264",
    "original": " of armor on head hits.",
    "translation": "",
    "context": "\"[$ $|Skill+pound] ignores an additional \" + getroottable().MSU.Text.colorPositive(\"+10%\") + \" of armor on head hits.\""
  },
  {
    "key": "d189c5fc07eda2919a8e1ab9ad0372291a75581cd8d003ca4e67ccdc93e02f25",
    "original": " of built [Fatigue|Concept.Fatigue] and gain the [$ $|Skill+adrenaline_effect] effect.",
    "translation": "",
    "context": "\"If the student dies, this character will immediately recover \" + getroottable().MSU.Text.colorPositive(\"50%\") + \" of built [Fatigue|Concept.Fatigue] and gain the [$ $|Skill+adrenaline_effect] effect.\""
  },
  {
    "key": "8f4bd8a8b7a512cd06eda2c9412aeb0145f8e1d35e7450789334496e8f5bb685",
    "original": " of damage ignores armor.",
    "translation": "",
    "context": "\"While wielding a fencing type sword an additional \" + getroottable().MSU.Text.colorPositive(\"25%\") + \" of damage ignores armor.\""
  },
  {
    "key": "f9469c71c0f7d21f248651e06e5788eb0b7f14ff18e478c97e88f2601c90e298",
    "original": " of the current durability of the armor piece hit.",
    "translation": "",
    "context": "\"Armor penetrating damage received is reduced by a percentage equal to \" + getroottable().MSU.Text.colorPositive(\"10%\") + \" of the current durability of the armor piece hit.\""
  },
  {
    "key": "8afd9af66312fc79a2d797fd1037458951f8a4fb205f302f84636597ee23bbb7",
    "original": " of the current total armor value of both body and head armor.",
    "translation": "",
    "context": "\"Armor damage taken is reduced by a percentage equal to \" + getroottable().MSU.Text.colorPositive(\"5%\") + \" of the current total armor value of both body and head armor.\""
  },
  {
    "key": "52484f2ba177d8c2414244ec86b75a1a84436cb054ed3beb2c4b46672c7f2796",
    "original": " of the stacks gained during the previous [turn|Concept.Turn] as additional [Action Points|Concept.ActionPoints] and attacks build up ",
    "translation": "",
    "context": "\"During a [turn|Concept.Turn] gain \" + getroottable().MSU.Text.colorPositive(\"half\") + \" of the stacks gained during the previous [turn|Concept.Turn] as additional [Action Points|Concept.ActionPoints] and attacks build up \" + getroottable().MSU.Text.colorPositive(\"5%\") + \" less [Fatigue|Concept.Fatigue] per such stack.\""
  },
  {
    "key": "90ea7a2dda31d2405dffa2577022f93a2a7bea33804669566e41e8ca3c032e86",
    "original": " of the user's [Resolve|Concept.Bravery].",
    "translation": "",
    "context": "\"When used on an adjacent target, reduces their [Melee Defense|Concept.MeleeDefense] and [Ranged Defense|Concept.RangeDefense] by \" + getroottable().MSU.Text.colorPositive(\"20%\") + \" of the user's [Resolve|Concept.Bravery].\""
  },
  {
    "key": "e3124668fed3acc2dbf522810e6523996a4b8f8cbaf43c1d523f9aafbc69387d",
    "original": " of their respective base values.",
    "translation": "",
    "context": "\"[Hitpoints|Concept.Hitpoints] and [Maximum Fatigue|Concept.MaximumFatigue] are increased by \" + getroottable().MSU.Text.colorPositive(\"10%\") + \" of their respective base values.\""
  },
  {
    "key": "6fb8378a4f3825f522e36a0fcd13d271b4b8b68bc1e616befc9e024308c9eea6",
    "original": " of your Base [Ranged Skill|Concept.RangeSkill] as additional Minimum and Maximum Damage.",
    "translation": "",
    "context": "\"Gain \" + getroottable().MSU.Text.colorPositive(\"10%\") + \" of your Base [Ranged Skill|Concept.RangeSkill] as additional Minimum and Maximum Damage.\""
  },
  {
    "key": "d4c03a7b920efdb9790082e7480c9c51850d19f8b277ad2aca1051c4b7da7592",
    "original": " of your Base [Ranged Skill|Concept.RangeSkill] as additional [Melee Skill|Concept.MeleeSkill] and [Melee Defense|Concept.MeleeDefense].",
    "translation": "",
    "context": "\"Gain \" + getroottable().MSU.Text.colorPositive(\"10%\") + \" of your Base [Ranged Skill|Concept.RangeSkill] as additional [Melee Skill|Concept.MeleeSkill] and [Melee Defense|Concept.MeleeDefense].\""
  },
  {
    "key": "6aafb61270451c59c057774977641b6f8d3c7c64ab9ca120a1f20aebc0e5efd9",
    "original": " of your [Maximum Fatigue|Concept.MaximumFatigue] after gear.",
    "translation": "",
    "context": "\"Fatigue Recovery is increased by \" + getroottable().MSU.Text.colorPositive(\"5%\") + \" of your [Maximum Fatigue|Concept.MaximumFatigue] after gear.\""
  },
  {
    "key": "eebde2e257ad69963f0e549358c3f7dcc19e4fe7dd4febe936d779aa8eadd150",
    "original": " of your [Melee Skill|Concept.MeleeSkill].",
    "translation": "",
    "context": "\"Unlocks the [$ $|Skill+rf_between_the_eyes_skill] skill which can be used to perform your primary attack with an additional chance to hit the head equal to \" + getroottable().MSU.Text.colorPositive(\"50%\") + \" of your [Melee Skill|Concept.MeleeSkill].\""
  },
  {
    "key": "18df75872a4f5034710ef8c170d8d585bef243a510f1176e08cef26765ab1f61",
    "original": " of your [Resolve|Concept.Bravery].",
    "translation": "",
    "context": "\"These morale checks now have an additional penalty to [Resolve|Concept.Bravery] of \" + getroottable().MSU.Text.colorPositive(\"20%\") + \" of your [Resolve|Concept.Bravery].\""
  },
  {
    "key": "c603590c03182f2f7714987723c349ba02c905a7ec9dd340b90048164872deca",
    "original": " of your current [Melee Skill|Concept.MeleeSkill] as additional chance to hit.",
    "translation": "",
    "context": "\"Throwing attacks gain \" + getroottable().MSU.Text.colorPositive(\"20%\") + \" of your current [Melee Skill|Concept.MeleeSkill] as additional chance to hit.\""
  },
  {
    "key": "0ac8be957ebe293766923cbaaf054dec334f25e5457686412b2537ea9f8b7d84",
    "original": " of your current [Melee Skill|Concept.MeleeSkill] to target the body part with the lower armor.",
    "translation": "",
    "context": "\"Attacks have a chance equal to \" + getroottable().MSU.Text.colorPositive(\"66%\") + \" of your current [Melee Skill|Concept.MeleeSkill] to target the body part with the lower armor.\""
  },
  {
    "key": "925ff42e30a7148df9a4fa5efef53a87e6fe756d72369b4a62c90f2f98e6543f",
    "original": " of your current combined head and body armor durability as [Resolve|Concept.Bravery] during [morale checks|Concept.Morale]. This is doubled against negative [morale checks|Concept.Morale].",
    "translation": "",
    "context": "\"Gain \" + getroottable().MSU.Text.colorPositive(\"5%\") + \" of your current combined head and body armor durability as [Resolve|Concept.Bravery] during [morale checks|Concept.Morale]. This is doubled against negative [morale checks|Concept.Morale].\""
  },
  {
    "key": "bfb1d044f90f4f147c1f0bc2c276a38b8889d7ada55ca90ddf2a788a2684a9e9",
    "original": " of your remaining [Action Points|Concept.ActionPoints], rounded down, as additional [Action Points|Concept.ActionPoints] during your next [turn|Concept.Turn].",
    "translation": "",
    "context": "\"At the end of your [turn|Concept.Turn], gain \" + getroottable().MSU.Text.colorPositive(\"half\") + \" of your remaining [Action Points|Concept.ActionPoints], rounded down, as additional [Action Points|Concept.ActionPoints] during your next [turn|Concept.Turn].\""
  },
  {
    "key": "ac3b14ef823c0bbe9c5f46c50ac78fe6f56b2a44b2ecab89f08b8a40672c5c4c",
    "original": " on a hit. This can stack up to ",
    "translation": "",
    "context": "\"Whenever you are attacked, gain a stacking bonus to [Melee Defense|Concept.MeleeDefense] and [Ranged Defense|Concept.RangeDefense] of \" + getroottable().MSU.Text.colorPositive(\"+2\") + \" on a miss and \" + getroottable().MSU.Text.colorPositive(\"+5\") + \" on a hit. This can stack up to \" + getroottable().MSU.Text.colorPositive(\"5\") + \" times for misses and up to \" + getroottable().MSU.Text.colorPositive(\"2\") + \" times for hits.\""
  },
  {
    "key": "bc52ef5a69851b3622bc8c02bc388ad129d290f47e3d956c3b2ee4c6d801ddb3",
    "original": " on a miss and ",
    "translation": "",
    "context": "\"Whenever you are attacked, gain a stacking bonus to [Melee Defense|Concept.MeleeDefense] and [Ranged Defense|Concept.RangeDefense] of \" + getroottable().MSU.Text.colorPositive(\"+2\") + \" on a miss and \" + getroottable().MSU.Text.colorPositive(\"+5\") + \" on a hit. This can stack up to \" + getroottable().MSU.Text.colorPositive(\"5\") + \" times for misses and up to \" + getroottable().MSU.Text.colorPositive(\"2\") + \" times for hits.\""
  },
  {
    "key": "7fb33133a496cac15d66375c4e9ca003652af5ef754109797ca748241fb67076",
    "original": " only.",
    "translation": "",
    "context": "\"Once the total bonus reaches \" + getroottable().MSU.Text.colorPositive(15) + \", all subsequent attacks increase it by \" + getroottable().MSU.Text.colorPositive(\"+1\") + \" only.\""
  },
  {
    "key": "cdd10ec98e8f8c5ee17d549ac3d11346c92a97eb82dbbb406a15d6180a7d2b3d",
    "original": " or more [Fatigue|Concept.Fatigue] built and remains disabled until you use [$ $|Skill+recover_skill].",
    "translation": "",
    "context": "\"The effect becomes disabled if you start a [turn|Concept.Turn] with \" + getroottable().MSU.Text.colorNegative(\"30%\") + \" or more [Fatigue|Concept.Fatigue] built and remains disabled until you use [$ $|Skill+recover_skill].\""
  },
  {
    "key": "ab7949a725b1d87dd39278621a02086cf5a3f9721376d9cf710c5262d081ea3a",
    "original": " otherwise.",
    "translation": "",
    "context": "\"Against targets who are not in cover, gain \" + getroottable().MSU.Text.colorPositive(\"+10%\") + \" armor penetration when using a bow and \" + getroottable().MSU.Text.colorPositive(\"+20%\") + \" otherwise.\""
  },
  {
    "key": "d72a44dfc07a3df79a2a2c47903abef4f19bc8913ae5aca9697459f573262948",
    "original": " perk points upon completing your next 5 [levels|Concept.Level] after picking this perk.",
    "translation": "",
    "context": "\"Gain \" + getroottable().MSU.Text.colorPositive(2) + \" perk points upon completing your next 5 [levels|Concept.Level] after picking this perk.\""
  },
  {
    "key": "6eb44cb70d91be7a1690dc6069ffc229f7c215db3ad15cf15cbe32d45ff9cbe4",
    "original": " random Shared Perk Group.",
    "translation": "",
    "context": "\"Gain \" + getroottable().MSU.Text.colorPositive(\"1\") + \" random Shared Perk Group.\""
  },
  {
    "key": "eb0c790d14296020b57076dfd9d461e9c07bc7c350e71a4f0c7bca328b881bc5",
    "original": " random Weapon Perk Groups.",
    "translation": "",
    "context": "\"Gain \" + getroottable().MSU.Text.colorPositive(\"2\") + \" random Weapon Perk Groups.\""
  },
  {
    "key": "388ffeb026c3e3bfdc57f786ec5e9e93dc48b43a25d2600e2752b754518064cb",
    "original": " reduced [threshold|Concept.InjuryThreshold] to inflict [injuries|Concept.InjuryTemporary] when attacking a [$ $|Skill+rf_rattled_effect], [$ $|Skill+stunned_effect], [$ $|Skill+dazed_effect], [$ $|Skill+net_effect], [$ $|Skill+sleeping_effect], [$ $|Skill+staggered_effect], [$ $|Skill+web_effect], or [$ $|Skill+rooted_effect] target.",
    "translation": "",
    "context": "\"Gain \" + getroottable().MSU.Text.colorPositive(\"+15%\") + \" chance to hit the head and \" + getroottable().MSU.Text.colorPositive(\"33%\") + \" reduced [threshold|Concept.InjuryThreshold] to inflict [injuries|Concept.InjuryTemporary] when attacking a [$ $|Skill+rf_rattled_effect], [$ $|Skill+stunned_effect], [$ $|Skill+dazed_effect], [$ $|Skill+net_effect], [$ $|Skill+sleeping_effect], [$ $|Skill+staggered_effect], [$ $|Skill+web_effect], or [$ $|Skill+rooted_effect] target.\""
  },
  {
    "key": "9242258f820f3830dcda46c72653727f6a70b7f77fb5164f577d6df229e8af16",
    "original": " reduced [threshold|Concept.InjuryThreshold] to inflict [injury|Concept.InjuryTemporary] and will inflict [$ $|Skill+bleeding_effect]. If any of the attacks inflicted an [injury|Concept.InjuryTemporary]., the attacks inflict additional [$ $|Skill+bleeding_effect].",
    "translation": "",
    "context": "\"During your [turn|Concept.Turn], after a successful attack against a target, all subsequent attacks have a \" + getroottable().MSU.Text.colorNegative(\"33%\") + \" reduced [threshold|Concept.InjuryThreshold] to inflict [injury|Concept.InjuryTemporary] and will inflict [$ $|Skill+bleeding_effect]. If any of the attacks inflicted an [injury|Concept.InjuryTemporary]., the attacks inflict additional [$ $|Skill+bleeding_effect].\""
  },
  {
    "key": "3153bd3b4beccd672e01d89b349e985097b651b5e6bb198f607d16ec33ff08b5",
    "original": " reduced chance to inflict friendly fire.",
    "translation": "",
    "context": "\"Ranged attacks have a \" + getroottable().MSU.Text.colorPositive(\"50%\") + \" reduced chance to inflict friendly fire.\""
  },
  {
    "key": "6625192509d35884bd933ce3152db9d98cbc56b6e7315b65e32d4e0f272e3ce3",
    "original": " reduced damage.",
    "translation": "",
    "context": "\"During your turn, attacks have a \" + getroottable().MSU.Text.colorPositive(\"50%\") + \" chance to perform a free extra attack of the same type with \" + getroottable().MSU.Text.colorNegative(\"50%\") + \" reduced damage.\""
  },
  {
    "key": "0f6a11f4c66fdc8faaa6c2e96232d4f97e94fced2ff511dc2d49f9fb681b2cda",
    "original": " reduction to the [Fatigue|Concept.Fatigue] cost of skills until the end of your next [turn|Concept.Turn], up to a maximum of ",
    "translation": "",
    "context": "\"Whenever you attack or are attacked, hit or miss, gain a stacking \" + getroottable().MSU.Text.colorPositive(\"+5\") + \" [Initiative|Concept.Initiative] and \" + getroottable().MSU.Text.colorPositive(\"+5%\") + \" reduction to the [Fatigue|Concept.Fatigue] cost of skills until the end of your next [turn|Concept.Turn], up to a maximum of \" + getroottable().MSU.Text.colorPositive(\"+25\") + \" and \" + getroottable().MSU.Text.colorPositive(\"+25%\") + \" respectively.\""
  },
  {
    "key": "18ab1a21f57ea6ba7e458db71d481064986a06a4add3d2626cb9c6c40054634f",
    "original": " respectively.",
    "translation": "",
    "context": "\"Whenever you attack or are attacked, hit or miss, gain a stacking \" + getroottable().MSU.Text.colorPositive(\"+5\") + \" [Initiative|Concept.Initiative] and \" + getroottable().MSU.Text.colorPositive(\"+5%\") + \" reduction to the [Fatigue|Concept.Fatigue] cost of skills until the end of your next [turn|Concept.Turn], up to a maximum of \" + getroottable().MSU.Text.colorPositive(\"+25\") + \" and \" + getroottable().MSU.Text.colorPositive(\"+25%\") + \" respectively.\""
  },
  {
    "key": "c8c4e1411bfee849b4917bd9e981ea1e75a5f36398cbc449880bd109c75cb9be",
    "original": " stack at the start of every [turn|Concept.Turn].",
    "translation": "",
    "context": "\"You lose \" + getroottable().MSU.Text.colorNegative(\"1\") + \" stack at the start of every [turn|Concept.Turn].\""
  },
  {
    "key": "2068b2eec8c0adb043c23bb0ad5c29cbdb9542e54a3f25d5bb769ae04e14aa89",
    "original": " stack for every hit or miss against any target during your [turn|Concept.Turn].",
    "translation": "",
    "context": "\"Gain \" + getroottable().MSU.Text.colorPositive(1) + \" stack for every hit or miss against any target during your [turn|Concept.Turn].\""
  },
  {
    "key": "bc696abfb597e405ae390c57a10cd06b0b9de246cca439e1ec8471ef293dd221",
    "original": " stack upon ending a [turn|Concept.Turn] without having attacked.",
    "translation": "",
    "context": "\"Lose \" + getroottable().MSU.Text.colorNegative(1) + \" stack upon ending a [turn|Concept.Turn] without having attacked.\""
  },
  {
    "key": "949c9c80841fdad62241430a5d2106563a018afc244dfc5455f10ba188d9e2a2",
    "original": " stacking [additively|Concept.StackAdditively].",
    "translation": "",
    "context": "\"For each stack [Resolve|Concept.Bravery], [Initiative|Concept.Initiative] and [Fatigue Recovery|Concept.FatigueRecovery] rate are increased by \" + getroottable().MSU.Text.colorPositive(\"15%\") + \" stacking [additively|Concept.StackAdditively].\""
  },
  {
    "key": "0161d0eb3d740134bc802f3e11cf3aedee00468961da46304d8a942f70922d26",
    "original": " stacks of Bloodlust, up to a maximum of 2 stacks.",
    "translation": "",
    "context": "\"After inflicting a fatality, gain \" + getroottable().MSU.Text.colorPositive(\"2\") + \" stacks of Bloodlust, up to a maximum of 2 stacks.\""
  },
  {
    "key": "00493f0c2faea96210e7363c23afb83d18f8848992033fd7d9936a6e26bb6d14",
    "original": " tile.",
    "translation": "",
    "context": "\"When using a two-handed fencing sword, the range of [$ $|Skill+lunge_skill] is increased by \" + getroottable().MSU.Text.colorPositive(1) + \" tile.\""
  },
  {
    "key": "86addf5787bb93edd5c5a9e8bae5ff0847f1bd415c14bd11aaeb1680ab3a3e14",
    "original": " times for hits.",
    "translation": "",
    "context": "\"Whenever you are attacked, gain a stacking bonus to [Melee Defense|Concept.MeleeDefense] and [Ranged Defense|Concept.RangeDefense] of \" + getroottable().MSU.Text.colorPositive(\"+2\") + \" on a miss and \" + getroottable().MSU.Text.colorPositive(\"+5\") + \" on a hit. This can stack up to \" + getroottable().MSU.Text.colorPositive(\"5\") + \" times for misses and up to \" + getroottable().MSU.Text.colorPositive(\"2\") + \" times for hits.\""
  },
  {
    "key": "2ee7791c00d7ecd02f6ec522a08c73458560de41c1b91a92b22b801906ed4e5d",
    "original": " times for misses and up to ",
    "translation": "",
    "context": "\"Whenever you are attacked, gain a stacking bonus to [Melee Defense|Concept.MeleeDefense] and [Ranged Defense|Concept.RangeDefense] of \" + getroottable().MSU.Text.colorPositive(\"+2\") + \" on a miss and \" + getroottable().MSU.Text.colorPositive(\"+5\") + \" on a hit. This can stack up to \" + getroottable().MSU.Text.colorPositive(\"5\") + \" times for misses and up to \" + getroottable().MSU.Text.colorPositive(\"2\") + \" times for hits.\""
  },
  {
    "key": "87721689ee42f4415e4afe0d0f0a84d4cd837dd0c66635bd0734127ee0e0b5b7",
    "original": " to ",
    "translation": "",
    "context": "\"Attacks have a random \" + getroottable().MSU.Text.colorPositive(\"+10%\") + \" to \" + getroottable().MSU.Text.colorPositive(\"+25%\") + \" armor penetration.\""
  },
  {
    "key": "87721689ee42f4415e4afe0d0f0a84d4cd837dd0c66635bd0734127ee0e0b5b7",
    "original": " to ",
    "translation": "",
    "context": "\"The penalty to hitchance when shooting at a target you have no clear line of shooting to is reduced from \" + getroottable().MSU.Text.colorNegative(\"75%\") + \" to \" + getroottable().MSU.Text.colorNegative(\"50%\") + \".\""
  },
  {
    "key": "87721689ee42f4415e4afe0d0f0a84d4cd837dd0c66635bd0734127ee0e0b5b7",
    "original": " to ",
    "translation": "",
    "context": "\"The drop in shield defense bonus at maximum [fatigue|Concept.Fatigue] is reduced from \" + getroottable().MSU.Text.colorNegative(\"50%\") + \" to \" + getroottable().MSU.Text.colorNegative(\"25%\") + \".\""
  },
  {
    "key": "9ca12239c7e02a1c5fde4afd5aee6023455deeab5487c1c6d9d98bbe075c11de",
    "original": " to a minimum of ",
    "translation": "",
    "context": "\"A successful attack with your mainhand dagger reduces the [Action Point|Concept.ActionPoints] cost of all its skills by \" + getroottable().MSU.Text.colorPositive(\"2\") + \" to a minimum of \" + getroottable().MSU.Text.colorPositive(\"2\") + \" for the remainder of this [turn|Concept.Turn].\""
  },
  {
    "key": "9ca12239c7e02a1c5fde4afd5aee6023455deeab5487c1c6d9d98bbe075c11de",
    "original": " to a minimum of ",
    "translation": "",
    "context": "\"For every 2 tiles moved, the [Action Point|Concept.ActionPoints] cost of your next attack is reduced by \" + getroottable().MSU.Text.colorPositive(1) + \" to a minimum of \" + getroottable().MSU.Text.colorPositive(1) + \", and the [Fatigue|Concept.Fatigue] cost is reduced by \" + getroottable().MSU.Text.colorPositive(\"10%\") + \".\""
  },
  {
    "key": "264c05d8327825a878946353060bf81158a6011b977f1c35c0dc8e07993a1504",
    "original": " to a minimum of 2 [Action Points|Concept.ActionPoints] per tile, and [Fatigue|Concept.Fatigue] cost is reduced to half.",
    "translation": "",
    "context": "\"[Action Point|Concept.ActionPoints] costs for movement on all terrain is reduced by \" + getroottable().MSU.Text.colorPositive(\"1\") + \" to a minimum of 2 [Action Points|Concept.ActionPoints] per tile, and [Fatigue|Concept.Fatigue] cost is reduced to half.\""
  },
  {
    "key": "005d36f4a02ea2c281452e852ebf8aa378fc04e27d14edd13cea8a11e841477d",
    "original": " to a minimum of 3.",
    "translation": "",
    "context": "\"Using any skill that costs [Action Points|Concept.ActionPoints] reduces the [Action Point|Concept.ActionPoints] cost of all skills by \" + getroottable().MSU.Text.colorPositive(\"1\") + \" to a minimum of 3.\""
  },
  {
    "key": "36f811c7219b4284150fb08f07df16ad53d9127d4081bba1729ef7a7f949ed44",
    "original": " until your next [turn|Concept.Turn].",
    "translation": "",
    "context": "\"Every attack with flails increases your current [Reach|Concept.Reach] by \" + getroottable().MSU.Text.colorPositive(\"+1\") + \" until your next [turn|Concept.Turn].\""
  },
  {
    "key": "bca197991113f7e670846ca7097928eb81c7ac213ef3c6aa1debfc8c41ba09de",
    "original": " weight in your offhand, southern swords retain their double grip bonus and use [$ $|Skill+gash_skill] as their primary attack instead of [$ $|Skill+slash].",
    "translation": "",
    "context": "\"With less than \" + getroottable().MSU.Text.colorNegative(\"10\") + \" weight in your offhand, southern swords retain their double grip bonus and use [$ $|Skill+gash_skill] as their primary attack instead of [$ $|Skill+slash].\""
  },
  {
    "key": "7d74404c8a067e7a43af9de7f6c4c8df919af510310e08a0d7a77b429e3930c4",
    "original": " when attacking at a distance of 2 tiles and by ",
    "translation": "",
    "context": "\"Damage is increased by \" + getroottable().MSU.Text.colorPositive(\"30%\") + \" when attacking at a distance of 2 tiles and by \" + getroottable().MSU.Text.colorPositive(\"20%\") + \" when attacking at a distance of 3 tiles.\""
  },
  {
    "key": "3dd5fe8ff6d1761d9d5aceecc4b5cae230f7f68a379cbda045ee1cf0c061601b",
    "original": " when attacking at a distance of 3 tiles.",
    "translation": "",
    "context": "\"Damage is increased by \" + getroottable().MSU.Text.colorPositive(\"30%\") + \" when attacking at a distance of 2 tiles and by \" + getroottable().MSU.Text.colorPositive(\"20%\") + \" when attacking at a distance of 3 tiles.\""
  },
  {
    "key": "c6e2ef50bf3451874c01e0368fb8850422729484a2828a7de0b750e01bf69d55",
    "original": " while you have at least 1 stack.",
    "translation": "",
    "context": "\"[Resolve|Concept.Bravery] and [Initiative|Concept.Initiative] are both increased by \" + getroottable().MSU.Text.colorPositive(\"15%\") + \" while you have at least 1 stack.\""
  },
  {
    "key": "e4f3671210a2f5d7154f3de1285785e19b28dc3caa344bf6674a8664ada059a5",
    "original": "'Can't fight if they can't walk.'",
    "translation": "",
    "context": "Fluff = \"'Can't fight if they can't walk.'\""
  },
  {
    "key": "8a99369db0a90d19cbe715217752d4e852a8803516953adf54079f68642fec82",
    "original": "'Give their 'ed a nice knock, then move in for the kill!'",
    "translation": "",
    "context": "Fluff = \"'Give their 'ed a nice knock, then move in for the kill!'\""
  },
  {
    "key": "ac0a18748588b93182631c75714cfc8da3252f3c651252c3fd868bb18e0d248f",
    "original": "'Hatchet, throwing axe, spear, javelin... they all kill just the same!'",
    "translation": "",
    "context": "Fluff = \"'Hatchet, throwing axe, spear, javelin... they all kill just the same!'\""
  },
  {
    "key": "63479e27b26228992d3c373b65e0b1e5635dadbae0bda71fc297c6dc55617885",
    "original": "'I can take it!'",
    "translation": "",
    "context": "Fluff = \"'I can take it!'\""
  },
  {
    "key": "3a11144c3ec412f89000ac957cd3e8d309cefd9404661650ad248f170616bf4b",
    "original": "'I'm not lootin' Captain! Just grabbing my javelin!'",
    "translation": "",
    "context": "Fluff = \"'I'm not lootin' Captain! Just grabbing my javelin!'\""
  },
  {
    "key": "6aeaa00482a09acf580bd887fdcbf2ce0fc0bb580064bb6230154fdecf5ce5ca",
    "original": "'If the target is watchin' the head of yer pike, they're sure not watchin' their back!'",
    "translation": "",
    "context": "Fluff = \"'If the target is watchin' the head of yer pike, they're sure not watchin' their back!'\""
  },
  {
    "key": "6392b60649de720d2bc273d605f6acb28fee8c2b34aa3fe6e97676ae24aced34",
    "original": "'It's not uncommon to make it to the end of the battle not remembering any details, just that you slew many men!'",
    "translation": "",
    "context": "Fluff = \"'It's not uncommon to make it to the end of the battle not remembering any details, just that you slew many men!'\""
  },
  {
    "key": "68c598b92159938df904be44de6309f35e6c70cfc6f52fdfcbc0ddfebb000729",
    "original": "'Let me take you on a trip to the floor.'",
    "translation": "",
    "context": "Fluff = \"'Let me take you on a trip to the floor.'\""
  },
  {
    "key": "a2e94d839e9956a2db91148352e10ffb70b6f86b85803b68dd26590fa7d75dd0",
    "original": "'Make way for the bad guy!'",
    "translation": "",
    "context": "Fluff = \"'Make way for the bad guy!'\""
  },
  {
    "key": "46c49c21ebc6216a4c80c3c5166decc1de8ef446132ba40cac09898010c75954",
    "original": "'Mountains cannot be moved, nor taken down!'",
    "translation": "",
    "context": "Fluff = \"'Mountains cannot be moved, nor taken down!'\""
  },
  {
    "key": "58f40499f601eaa949ccc1e350eda494e62818ba35520b6b41c21347181b25a6",
    "original": "'My projectiles find their own way'",
    "translation": "",
    "context": "Fluff = \"'My projectiles find their own way'\""
  },
  {
    "key": "fbc6c9827d20f4b9efdd147873370de2c242b7258e617b64605acd2de6e2f7e7",
    "original": "'Not much to be afraid of behind a suit of plate!'",
    "translation": "",
    "context": "Fluff = \"'Not much to be afraid of behind a suit of plate!'\""
  },
  {
    "key": "30c180c37e85c65fb2da25cee2a6386fa36890108dcfab58ec062b09e9bf95b8",
    "original": "'Off with their heads!'",
    "translation": "",
    "context": "Fluff = \"'Off with their heads!'\""
  },
  {
    "key": "4ca8cffcb889727ccef854e0e2e68e3b7ee643c3678d032431954d5b35fa7ed0",
    "original": "'On the battlefield, you must always be ready to defend at a moment's notice, or strike at a narrow opportunity!'",
    "translation": "",
    "context": "Fluff = \"'On the battlefield, you must always be ready to defend at a moment's notice, or strike at a narrow opportunity!'\""
  },
  {
    "key": "dc2dfc86088c0164dfd805b8b0244c9301943d6e9ab1f9248024210ee4469c64",
    "original": "'One javelin to the head will take 'em right out!'",
    "translation": "",
    "context": "Fluff = \"'One javelin to the head will take 'em right out!'\""
  },
  {
    "key": "4c6a6ee8aced2a8c43cc0088f8c41a5cfaa9bd5c8bda30915351ad651b71532a",
    "original": "'Roll out the barrel, feel it in your bones!'",
    "translation": "",
    "context": "Fluff = \"'Roll out the barrel, feel it in your bones!'\""
  },
  {
    "key": "14284bda4ffb4be946494e45ef071f011de6e6d5e9b9b10860534b27eb31a2ae",
    "original": "'S' is the symbol for 'Hope'",
    "translation": "",
    "context": "Fluff = \"'S' is the symbol for 'Hope'\""
  },
  {
    "key": "ef61fc0371fc565bf500be93c30f009f02814639ee496d555eec10d1006b8ec1",
    "original": "'Teach a man to fish and he'll be worth his salt to the end of his days.'",
    "translation": "",
    "context": "Fluff = \"'Teach a man to fish and he'll be worth his salt to the end of his days.'\""
  },
  {
    "key": "58f19eb8ceff04f490ed48f7c8ed99c31103b5628f19534444c5569ad072d546",
    "original": "'When your buddy's hittin' 'em, you hit 'em too!'",
    "translation": "",
    "context": "Fluff = \"'When your buddy's hittin' 'em, you hit 'em too!'\""
  },
  {
    "key": "8be630116249f1dc76bf2403322437a0d30818b7f1f2da67b88fb5c887e46253",
    "original": "'Who's this chunk of meat?'",
    "translation": "",
    "context": "Fluff = \"'Who's this chunk of meat?'\""
  },
  {
    "key": "3e50961952eaa51ab954a3d930d0d2e03635637112c1e7142d648d095ff9e2dc",
    "original": "'Yeah, skill doesn't mean so much when you're surrounded by 10 angry townsfolk with sharp pitchforks!'",
    "translation": "",
    "context": "Fluff = \"'Yeah, skill doesn't mean so much when you're surrounded by 10 angry townsfolk with sharp pitchforks!'\""
  },
  {
    "key": "45777805b47caee9e5fe1bb8614e5b663c1bd3ef19c77822b4a09146204ea8b0",
    "original": "'You shall do it!'",
    "translation": "",
    "context": "Fluff = \"'You shall do it!'\""
  },
  {
    "key": "ef30da2bcbd99b064e0d4a9676c93e6a5b6ea81a54479cf3ad63f838c53d9dd7",
    "original": ", all subsequent attacks increase it by ",
    "translation": "",
    "context": "\"Once the total bonus reaches \" + getroottable().MSU.Text.colorPositive(15) + \", all subsequent attacks increase it by \" + getroottable().MSU.Text.colorPositive(\"+1\") + \" only.\""
  },
  {
    "key": "f493ec9e68903d5b6d4787b4f7c66565913cccdfd9bffc74016e5389e09d4ddf",
    "original": ", and the [Fatigue|Concept.Fatigue] cost is reduced by ",
    "translation": "",
    "context": "\"For every 2 tiles moved, the [Action Point|Concept.ActionPoints] cost of your next attack is reduced by \" + getroottable().MSU.Text.colorPositive(1) + \" to a minimum of \" + getroottable().MSU.Text.colorPositive(1) + \", and the [Fatigue|Concept.Fatigue] cost is reduced by \" + getroottable().MSU.Text.colorPositive(\"10%\") + \".\""
  },
  {
    "key": "7378611b6077f0802e781ac9d01ffb4e6d81f81c7adc8ed7553d147c8103abb8",
    "original": ", up to a maximum of 70%.",
    "translation": "",
    "context": "\"Each stack of rage increases [Resolve|Concept.Bravery] and [Initiative|Concept.Initiative] by \" + getroottable().MSU.Text.colorPositive(\"+2\") + \" and Melee Damage by \" + getroottable().MSU.Text.colorPositive(\"2%\") + \". Each stack lowers [Melee Defense|Concept.MeleeDefense] by \" + getroottable().MSU.Text.colorNegative(\"-1\") + \" and lowers damage received by \" + getroottable().MSU.Text.colorPositive(\"2%\") + \", up to a maximum of 70%.\""
  },
  {
    "key": "3b1c337ed18b8594673c4bbceca0f2fabc259e2d7b74c8925c6718326b835755",
    "original": ", without diminishing returns, against enemies in your [Zone of Control|Concept.ZoneOfControl] until they hit you. After being hit this effect expires, but is reset if the [Zone of Control|Concept.ZoneOfControl] is broken.",
    "translation": "",
    "context": "\"The bonus from each point of [Reach Advantage|Concept.ReachAdvantage] you have is increased by \" + getroottable().MSU.Text.colorPositive(\"+2\") + \", without diminishing returns, against enemies in your [Zone of Control|Concept.ZoneOfControl] until they hit you. After being hit this effect expires, but is reset if the [Zone of Control|Concept.ZoneOfControl] is broken.\""
  },
  {
    "key": "3b4deef66b60f7b32d21bbcbdee969371d903bd5b0c0a72bcfe1dd903de3f0f5",
    "original": ". Additionally, the targeted enemies' [Reach|Concept.Reach] is reduced by ",
    "translation": "",
    "context": "\"AOE attacks, hit or miss, increase your [Reach|Concept.Reach] by \" + getroottable().MSU.Text.colorPositive(\"+3\") + \". Additionally, the targeted enemies' [Reach|Concept.Reach] is reduced by \" + getroottable().MSU.Text.colorPositive(\"-3\") + \" for their attacks against you.\""
  },
  {
    "key": "1f637f8e1c0182584f107303ac705628f23056c670bd0b8b72a5903d59a9d2d4",
    "original": ". Each stack lowers [Melee Defense|Concept.MeleeDefense] by ",
    "translation": "",
    "context": "\"Each stack of rage increases [Resolve|Concept.Bravery] and [Initiative|Concept.Initiative] by \" + getroottable().MSU.Text.colorPositive(\"+2\") + \" and Melee Damage by \" + getroottable().MSU.Text.colorPositive(\"2%\") + \". Each stack lowers [Melee Defense|Concept.MeleeDefense] by \" + getroottable().MSU.Text.colorNegative(\"-1\") + \" and lowers damage received by \" + getroottable().MSU.Text.colorPositive(\"2%\") + \", up to a maximum of 70%.\""
  },
  {
    "key": "e8952e664ce4ba5adc2a15c3d4d87ac05e646f3d45fcb8ea3b55f09f63b982d5",
    "original": ". This also applies to the additional defense bonus of the [$ $|Skill+shieldwall] skill.",
    "translation": "",
    "context": "\"The shield defense bonus is increased by \" + getroottable().MSU.Text.colorPositive(\"25%\") + \". This also applies to the additional defense bonus of the [$ $|Skill+shieldwall] skill.\""
  },
  {
    "key": "c1863cc302504a99ff0487803f261bdd616fbff627e7f6ecce1a80bef8188797",
    "original": ". This bonus is carried over into your next [turn|Concept.Turn] but only until the first skill used or upon [waiting|Concept.Wait] that [turn|Concept.Turn].",
    "translation": "",
    "context": "\"Each stack increases your [Initiative|Concept.Initiative] by \" + getroottable().MSU.Text.colorPositive(\"+15\") + \". This bonus is carried over into your next [turn|Concept.Turn] but only until the first skill used or upon [waiting|Concept.Wait] that [turn|Concept.Turn].\""
  },
  {
    "key": "c2de1c97b4a64526fa7cad9cdb33621a2a4dbf017ab71bc951bef995a17cf2db",
    "original": ". This effect only lasts until the end of your second [turn|Concept.Turn].",
    "translation": "",
    "context": "\"The first two throwing attacks during a battle have their [Action Point|Concept.ActionPoints] costs \" + getroottable().MSU.Text.colorPositive(\"halved\") + \". This effect only lasts until the end of your second [turn|Concept.Turn].\""
  },
  {
    "key": "9f21109282f4c7acc99adf61d473e28f9845fb6418294c2077c7765b0f1d6087",
    "original": ". This effect stacks with [$ $|Perk+perk_brawny].",
    "translation": "",
    "context": "\"The penalty to [Maximum Fatigue|Concept.MaximumFatigue] and [Initiative|Concept.Initiative] from equipped items in your head, body, mainhand and offhand slots is reduced by \" + getroottable().MSU.Text.colorPositive(\"20%\") + \". This effect stacks with [$ $|Perk+perk_brawny].\""
  },
  {
    "key": "406bc809d326c766fb6cd8ca958f8bf84b0cbaa11ce3e3759fa12186839c61a8",
    "original": "A [$ $|Skill+player_character_trait] has a ",
    "translation": "",
    "context": "\"A [$ $|Skill+player_character_trait] has a \" + getroottable().MSU.Text.colorPositive(\"100%\") + \" chance to succeed.\""
  },
  {
    "key": "9be602cac2fc1c615212d4563b0320bf9c1b187ab5d24fa75c990218f2211034",
    "original": "A corpse can only be used once per combat and cannot be used by multiple characters with this perk.",
    "translation": "",
    "context": ""
  },
  {
    "key": "f92f0f1f4abae5d3425228ac3c78892f89209df6d0847d54d55d9a924db2c94b",
    "original": "A friendly horn of war has never ceased to steel the hearts of men.",
    "translation": "",
    "context": "Fluff = \"A friendly horn of war has never ceased to steel the hearts of men.\""
  },
  {
    "key": "6b04a7b0fa9b7e49bafb79cd7765e360bc318b5100d3841c73166cebfb4aaae0",
    "original": "A low shield. A slobby stab. A fake stumble. All are ways that you've learned to tempt your opponent into a fatal false move!",
    "translation": "",
    "context": "Fluff = \"A low shield. A slobby stab. A fake stumble. All are ways that you've learned to tempt your opponent into a fatal false move!\""
  },
  {
    "key": "84f03bb8b7b69ab622d45c7474b668ac538138f323998f21653f91687b78c860",
    "original": "A partner's melee [AOE|Concept.AOE] attacks never have more than ",
    "translation": "",
    "context": "\"A partner's melee [AOE|Concept.AOE] attacks never have more than \" + getroottable().MSU.Text.colorPositive(getroottable().Const.Combat.MV_HitChanceMin + \"%\") + \" chance to hit their partner and inflict \" + getroottable().MSU.Text.colorPositive(\"50%\") + \" less damage.\""
  },
  {
    "key": "100ed3a45d81123228dce21edc1952f840a8d7498f12b3c62720083659f225f4",
    "original": "A strike to the head from this character means goodnight!",
    "translation": "",
    "context": "Fluff = \"A strike to the head from this character means goodnight!\""
  },
  {
    "key": "2dabb46529efc0652b50292ffc648dafed94a0d6b56507ba8c78e190d7547911",
    "original": "A successful attack with your mainhand dagger reduces the [Action Point|Concept.ActionPoints] cost of all its skills by ",
    "translation": "",
    "context": "\"A successful attack with your mainhand dagger reduces the [Action Point|Concept.ActionPoints] cost of all its skills by \" + getroottable().MSU.Text.colorPositive(\"2\") + \" to a minimum of \" + getroottable().MSU.Text.colorPositive(\"2\") + \" for the remainder of this [turn|Concept.Turn].\""
  },
  {
    "key": "bc7bf833b1a0e66b37097fc41b449f3d77b47190f596f12538137185e73071b5",
    "original": "A successful hit increases the damage of your next attack by ",
    "translation": "",
    "context": "\"A successful hit increases the damage of your next attack by \" + getroottable().MSU.Text.colorNegative(\"20%\") + \".\""
  },
  {
    "key": "52bd5ebb5ef886bf3ac097d8b09c1f88da2d6756695e2018d7addf4641f28a61",
    "original": "A sword, too, can take someone's head off just fine!",
    "translation": "",
    "context": "Fluff = \"A sword, too, can take someone's head off just fine!\""
  },
  {
    "key": "8ebb255f5a6a3da61fdbe423b5a4e87d01c18271ea8f057ea0459fa4baa2edfa",
    "original": "AOE attacks, hit or miss, increase your [Reach|Concept.Reach] by ",
    "translation": "",
    "context": "\"AOE attacks, hit or miss, increase your [Reach|Concept.Reach] by \" + getroottable().MSU.Text.colorPositive(\"+3\") + \". Additionally, the targeted enemies' [Reach|Concept.Reach] is reduced by \" + getroottable().MSU.Text.colorPositive(\"-3\") + \" for their attacks against you.\""
  },
  {
    "key": "2e24920a882e1a6a88c5ad8476cdd42bdca7b6da4b9e3860ebf53f48a98a1502",
    "original": "Additional damage ignores armor. This bonus is ",
    "translation": "",
    "context": "\"Additional damage ignores armor. This bonus is \" + getroottable().MSU.Text.colorPositive(\"25%\") + \" for one-handed weapons, \" + getroottable().MSU.Text.colorPositive(\"35%\") + \" for one-handed weapon with shield, and \" + getroottable().MSU.Text.colorPositive(\"15%\") + \" for two-handed weapons.\""
  },
  {
    "key": "e7ad684c0b9d528180eb5dcbbbac49616b8401b5713341f0490e34d857a35655",
    "original": "Adds the Cleaver perk group to this character's perk tree.",
    "translation": "",
    "context": ""
  },
  {
    "key": "2608729251008c9658e7d21d8041325c145bd07af6bb87c6a441153a37f79551",
    "original": "Adrenaline",
    "translation": "",
    "context": "Key = \"Adrenaline\""
  },
  {
    "key": "d3dc623e2dc6b4c8c5563a983fc6708fab6064e21253b60c52c86c464913fa24",
    "original": "After inflicting a fatality, gain ",
    "translation": "",
    "context": "\"After inflicting a fatality, gain \" + getroottable().MSU.Text.colorPositive(\"2\") + \" stacks of Bloodlust, up to a maximum of 2 stacks.\""
  },
  {
    "key": "2d0fd564f5358e483d6f14808d857ed09a5be3b48dac31ea099f95f12b5d2cdf",
    "original": "Against opponents who have missed a melee attack against you gain ",
    "translation": "",
    "context": "\"Against opponents who have missed a melee attack against you gain \" + getroottable().MSU.Text.colorPositive(\"+10%\") + \" chance to hit or ignore the defense granted by shield, whichever is greater, and deal \" + getroottable().MSU.Text.colorPositive(\"20%\") + \" more damage. Expires upon your next attack or [waiting|Concept.Wait] or ending your [turn|Concept.Turn].\""
  },
  {
    "key": "8be79e0e1e8333bc1fdd07b5199afc2c426f157c02a27c0dee594f9f500b21f9",
    "original": "Against targets who are not in cover, gain ",
    "translation": "",
    "context": "\"Against targets who are not in cover, gain \" + getroottable().MSU.Text.colorPositive(\"+10%\") + \" armor penetration when using a bow and \" + getroottable().MSU.Text.colorPositive(\"+20%\") + \" otherwise.\""
  },
  {
    "key": "b121dd9263be222a737ca1f0fd28dc939ec8750965aaa5dabefb3dcc38436fd9",
    "original": "All Attributes are increased by ",
    "translation": "",
    "context": "\"All Attributes are increased by \" + getroottable().MSU.Text.colorPositive(\"+15\") + \".\""
  },
  {
    "key": "c9172eae70147fa5ca5775f07984fa02758bb4ccc01f2785aff23e85e8ceff33",
    "original": "All attacks, melee or ranged, gain ",
    "translation": "",
    "context": "\"All attacks, melee or ranged, gain \" + getroottable().MSU.Text.colorPositive(\"+10%\") + \" chance to hit the head.\""
  },
  {
    "key": "a4ae7b5f30949a933a6b9ef95fc09ed7930c351766f3a9ec27a9ef8379b3e938",
    "original": "All skills with two-handed weapons, with a range of 2 tiles, having an [Action Point|Concept.ActionPoints] cost of ",
    "translation": "",
    "context": "\"All skills with two-handed weapons, with a range of 2 tiles, having an [Action Point|Concept.ActionPoints] cost of \" + getroottable().MSU.Text.colorNegative(\"6\") + \" have their [Action Point|Concept.ActionPoints] cost reduced to \" + getroottable().MSU.Text.colorNegative(\"5\") + \".\""
  },
  {
    "key": "5b53ffdfc3c29389ff11e2f0704a17a9cd4fa3f18436020a8fb100fa36cc4da5",
    "original": "All stacks are lost if you end your [turn|Concept.Turn] with more than half of your [Action Points|Concept.ActionPoints] remaining, use [Wait|Concept.Wait] or [$ $|Skill+recover_skill], or get [$ $|Skill+stunned_effect], rooted or [$ $|Skill+staggered_effect].",
    "translation": "",
    "context": ""
  },
  {
    "key": "951242f687ec7eb666a25edcaf52573eeb8c3928e1c29b64a55861930a307f2e",
    "original": "Allies with a shield will use [$ $|Skill+shieldwall] for free at the start of each battle.",
    "translation": "",
    "context": ""
  },
  {
    "key": "e8fdfd9b5ba9cce24c56df9f0ecb4b90e03c3c7d8ac0cf67d0c42b95515b441e",
    "original": "Allies within 2 tiles have the [Action Point|Concept.ActionPoints] and [Fatigue|Concept.Fatigue] costs of [$ $|Skill+shieldwall] halved. Cannot reduce the [Action Point|Concept.ActionPoints] cost below ",
    "translation": "",
    "context": "\"Allies within 2 tiles have the [Action Point|Concept.ActionPoints] and [Fatigue|Concept.Fatigue] costs of [$ $|Skill+shieldwall] halved. Cannot reduce the [Action Point|Concept.ActionPoints] cost below \" + getroottable().MSU.Text.colorNegative(2) + \".\""
  },
  {
    "key": "6bcb0285e4ca4408b294a2771088b422f89496feaf749dfbd14c4db1928537a6",
    "original": "Allows [$ $|Skill+rf_passing_step_skill] to be usable even while holding something, e.g. a shield, in your offhand.",
    "translation": "",
    "context": ""
  },
  {
    "key": "5b182a4cb75cd3e4adfdd2cc56386ff1ae8f41a692b32b6360a4a0b3e0f0ac72",
    "original": "Allows you to choose another member of your company as your partner. You will remain partners until one of you dies or leaves the company. You and your partner gain the following bonuses when there is no ally next to you or your partner.",
    "translation": "",
    "context": ""
  },
  {
    "key": "dfc2df341ba3cb5e0583d8e05443431354661dba3cf54d16aa3b0a21cf9c9271",
    "original": "Always start battles at Confident [morale|Concept.Morale].",
    "translation": "",
    "context": ""
  },
