    "translation": "",
    "context": ""
  },
  {
    "key": "c9e8ea4f335ea4ce9100a3cb0261f2c9693b6122358e2f00ffc709602631172a",
    "original": "Gain the first two [perks|Concept.Perk] in a random melee perk group that you have access to.",
