    "key": "7be9aba694a655e2280b6abc04be3bccd10d7c35187b9882e9bfa8ddacb7d597",
    "original": "Unlocks the [$ $|Skill+rf_command_skill] skill which allows you move allies forward in the turn order.",
    "translation": "",
